\id LUK
\ide UTF-8
\h Luka
\toc1 Luka
\toc2 Luka
\toc3 luk
\mt1 Luka
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nubo ɗuce wo tum nangen mulangka dor digero wo tim ɗong ɗong more beu,
\v 2 Nawo bou binen kang nubo wo kaba tom nuwe kanga nuweu kange cangatini kereu.
\v 3 La yilam yarak tak minen wori min fuwam ɗigero wiyak ki kaba, nan mulang mwen ɗigero wo wank ki wank nii la ɗureu Tiyofila.
\v 4 Nyori na mwi nyimon bilenke dikero ci merang mweneu.
\v 5 Ki kumeni Hiridu liya Yahuda, nii wabe kange wi dendo Zakariya wo mwanlor Abija; Wice Alicabatu ken naniyak Haruna.
\v 6 Gwam ce ci cak-cak ka kwama (ci manki) kurom mor werfun kange bidoti te luwe.
\v 7 Dila ciman ki bwe wori Alicabatu Combilome, ri cin cirarangum gwance.
\v 8 La kambo Zakariya ka kwama ma nangentini nii waberti wo bwangten cokka ce keu.
\v 9 Ki nure ciki bwangten de naci cok nii wabe wo a wabtiyeu, la cin cok co ki dajen naci doken mor bi kur wabe Teluwe naci tui nuwanko ficange.
\v 10 Mwerka nibe ko gwam kuob dilo ti kale ki kwama wo nuwanko ficangeu tui tiye.
\v 11 La bwetomange Teluweu cer cinen lan tiken cattiyer tancilan ficanger.
\v 12 Kambo Zakariya toceri, kwomco, la taito tanco.
\v 13 Dila bwe tomange kwama yico “Cuware tai Zakariya, wori cin nuwam dilo mweu. Wi mwe Alicabatu an bo mwen bwe. Mwi Co dencero Yowana.
\v 14 Mwan yikam ki bilangtum kange fuwor nere, la nubo kila a bilangti ki borcere.
\v 15 Wori Canyi lan ki dur kabuni Te-luwe. Mani co no mwem bi tuittuibti kaka diker no karo kwam kwame, Catin din ki yiwa tangbe ko wucakeu mor fwiye nece.
\v 16 Naniyak Iciraila ko duce wo a yila cuko Teluwe kwama Cenen.
\v 17 Can ya kabum Teluwe mo yu wa tangbo kange bikwan Iliyak, Na yilau ki ner tebembo bibeyo nen kange wo bongi nyeu na ya mor nyomka cak-cake -na ci Ywel te luwe nin nubo wo ci cok cineneu.”
\v 18 Zakariya yi Bwetanange wucake “Ma nyom dike wo nyi? wori min cele ri wimi coro kilam”.
\v 19 Nii tomangeu wucakeu Ciya yicoki “Mo Jibrai'lu, wo tire kabum kwamau. Cin tomu ye nami yinen ker, nan bo mwen ki kero lomlome.
\v 20 La to! Mwan yilam cōk, mani mwa dol tokka kere ti, dila diya dikero buro dimmeri ntimade. Wori mwi nebo bilenker ker miro nin, wo a diiti ki kwama dong-donge
\v 21 La nubo ningtang Zakariya ti. Cin nyimangi wori cinti lenger mor bikur waber.
\v 22 Dila ki kwa'ma ci ceruweri, dolbo yici ker. La ciin nyimom ki cin to dukum ki kwamawo ci mor bikur-wabereu. La cin nungkancinen ti ki kank worimani citok ker ti.
\v 23 La yilam kambo kumeni nanger cero cume ri, cin cu lo co.
\v 24 Kambo kume ni wo cumeri, wice Alicabatu tum fwer la cin yu rangum dorceri na cuwako nunge ce. Cin yiki,
\v 25 “Wo lo diker kwama mamene kambo ci toye ki corciniyeu, naci tum kwenduwe miu ka nobe.
\v 26 Ki ciwako nukkune, kwama tom nii tomange wuccake Jibrailu mor Cinanlor Galili ci coti ki Nazaret,
\v 27 bubiya nin wo cine ken nii kange wo den cero Yucufu, wo naniyak Dauda, la bubiya dendo Maryamu.
\v 28 Cin bow Cinenri ciki, “A Ysrumnen, mo wo fiya cini ducce! Teluwe wi kange mo”.
\v 29 La cin kulongum duce, ki kercero la cin kwabi, ya rume ye wo.
\v 30 Bwe tomange wuccake yicoki, “Cuware tai, Maryamu, wori mwin fiya cini kwama nin.
\v 31 To, mwan tu fwed ri na mwi bo bwe. Mwa cun den cero 'Yecu'.
\v 32 Can yilam nii dur la ci cuu ki Bibwe nii dur re. Teluwe kwama atin ne co kuti le liyare Tekwace Dauda.
\v 33 Can ma liyar dor lo Yakubu diiri, Liyar cero manki dika”.
\v 34 Maryamu me bibwetomange wuccake ki; “Dike wo a bwinyi la mi nyumumbo nii na bare wiyeu?”
\v 35 Bibwe tomange kwaama ciya ri yi co ki, “Yuwa tangba kwamako an bow mwinen, ri bi kwan nii dur reu atin bow dor mwer. La wucakke wo mwi bo tiyeu a coki Bibwe kwama.
\v 36 To, na niya mweko Alicabatu tu fwer ki ciraka ceko. Wo co cuwiyak ceko mukkune, co wo no ci cuoti ki combilomeu.
\v 37 Di kero kange mani wo mani a mati kabum kwama”.
\v 38 Maryamu yi ki, “To, min bubiya canga kwama. A yila men na tomange meu”. Dila bwe tomange kwama dob co.
\v 39 Dila Maryamu kweni ki kume tini co wulom wulom yaken mor bi ten kongtini, yaken bi ten Yahuda.
\v 40 Ciin yaken mor luwe Zakariya ri cin yarum Alicabatu.
\v 41 Yilam kambo Alicabatu nuwa yarume Maryamu ri bwe mor fwe ce mokangi la Alicabatu diim ki yuwa tangbako wucake.
\v 42 Ciin kung dir cero kibi kwan ciki, “Mwin nii bi bwiyere mor natube, ri nii bwiyere bwe wo mor fwiye meu.
\v 43 Ye bwi wo fiya yenye, la ne Te luwe mi a bou ti mi nene?
\v 44 La ta kambo diir yaru mer mwero bou tu miyeri bwe fwe.
\v 45 Nii bi bwiyere co nawiye wo ne bilenke ki digero wo ciyi co fiye kwama wiye atin dii me.
\v 46 Maryamu yiki “Dume miu caklang Te luwe
\v 47 re, yuwa tangba miu bilangi kwama nii cyer yerenin.
\v 48 Wori cin to cukka dorek bubiya canga ce. La to, nawo kange kab kaltini gwam a co yeki nii bi bwiyere.
\v 49 Wori co, wo nii bi kwaneu, ma men digero dur, la den cero wucak.
\v 50 Jire duwe ceu tii nyo kal ya ciko kaleu ki buro wo nuwa taicero tiyeu.
\v 51 Cin nung bi kwancero ki kank cek, cin yalum buro ki kunka duwek keu ki dike ci kwati neer cere.
\v 52 Cin cukkangum bi bei liyabbe dor kutile cero nin, la cin kungum nob fuebbo.
\v 53 Cin cam ki nob wurabbo ki diketi no ken, dila nubo cuwe cuweu cin yoken ci kang kwicer.
\v 54 Cin ne canga ce Iciraila tikali, nyori naci kwabi naci nung jire duwe
\v 55 (Nawo ci yi tebbe beu) ciyi Ibrahim kange naniyak ceke diri.
\v 56 Maryamu yi kange Alicabatu cuyako ta'ar ri cin yilaken lo co.
\v 57 La kwama bou na Alicabatu a bom bwi bwece, la cin bou bwe bwayile.
\v 58 Nubo bi dom kange ca kange na niyak ceko nuwa ki kwama nung cinen Jire duwe ce durko, la cin bilangi kange co.
\v 59 La yilam ki diye naruberi cin bow naci mwatum lar bwero. Ciikin cuom co “Zakariya”, na den te cero.
\v 60 Dila neele ciya ki o, onga. “A cuoco ki Yuwana”
\v 61 Cin yicoki, “Nii kange man mor naniya kumek wo cico tiki dendo we”.
\v 62 Cin nung tece ninki kang kambo ci cuiti naci ne co dendeu.
\v 63 Tece me ci ya neco ter mulankar la cin mulangi, “Den cero Yohanna”. Cin nyimangi gwam dor dikero wo.
\v 64 Dangjang dangjang nyi ceu wumom ri la biyen cero fiya cyer ka. cin tok ker la cin cak lang kwama.
\v 65 Taito bou dor nubo gwam wo yim Cunga cekeu. Kerowo yalati gwam mor biten kongni Yahuda.
\v 66 Nubo gwam wo nuwa ri, yoken mor nere ce, tokti ki “La ye bwewo a yila tiye?” La kang Te luwe ko wi kange co.
\v 67 Tece Zakariya diim ki yuwa tangbe ko wuccake la tok ker dukumer, ki
\v 68 “Caklanka fiye Teluwe wiye, kwama Iciraila, cin bow naci ma tikali la cinma nob cebo nin cerka.
\v 69 Cin kung binek cume fuloka lo canga ce Dauda,
\v 70 (nawo ci tokki nyi nob tomange ceu kwattiye),
\v 71 fuloka nob kiyeb beu kange nubo wo kwerbo nyeu.
\v 72 Can ma wuro naci nung, tebbe bo nin jire duwe ri la naci kwa nor cero wucak keu,
\v 73 weri wo ci yii tebo Ibrahim.
\v 74 Cii weri naci nebo co kambo ci cokum bo kange nob kiyeb bekeri, nabi bwangci nenten kibi kwan neret
\v 75 mor wucakke kange cak-cake kabum cem ki kumetinibeu kale we nin gwam.
\v 76 O, kange mo, bwe, ciya co nen ki bwe tomange nii durre, la mwan yaken kabum tikobe Te-luwe ri na mwi ywel nure ceu, na mwi ywel nubo ki boka ceko
\v 77 na ne nob cebo nyom ka fulokak ki tab ka bwirank kerer cero.
\v 78 Wo an bwi wori jire duwe kwama beu duwi kabo, wo kercer di filango ceru dii yeu atin bou na tikangbo,
\v 79 na ne filang ki nubo wo yim kumta cilenen kange kakulok bwareke. Ca tin ma wuro na bwangten ki nabe ko mor nure lima nereke
\v 80 La bweu dwi la yilam ki bi kwan mor yuwa tangba, la ciki no mor yere na nyimde diye ci ter cerkako yanglang Iciraila.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 La ki kumetini co, kaicar Augusta tung tomange cin toki ciki a kiyeu nubo gwam wo yim dor bitinereu.
\v 2 Won co kiye ka kaba maneu ki kwama wo kiriyuc ma liyar ti curiya.
\v 3 La nubo gwam yarangen cinanlor cer naci mulangum ki kiye kakor.
\v 4 Yucufu ken kwenu Galili wo mor cinanlor Nazaret la cin yaken Yahuza, cinanlor Dauda, wo cuoti Baitalomi, wori ciki no naniyak Dauda.
\v 5 Cin yaken wi naci mulangum dercero kange Maryamu wo ci bob beu la ki fwer.
\v 6 La kambo ci wi ye ri, kwama lam wo ci bom bwe tiye lam.
\v 7 Cii bo bwe bibare, bwe kaba ce, la cin kwomum co ki yilang ko cuwe mer la yoken co mor tokum nennem wori ci man ki fiye wi.
\v 8 La nob biyuwareb bo wi cungako co ci dami ner bitibere to bi cir cero ti ki kume.
\v 9 Bwe tomange Te luweu cer cinen, la duktangka Te luwek ko tebum cunga ceko, la cin dim ki tai ducce.
\v 10 Dila Bwe tomange kwama yici “Ko cuware tai, wori mi bo kumen ki kero ken wo a bou hi ki fuwor nerero dur nubo nin gwame.
\v 11 Duwen cin bo kimen nii fuloka mor cinan lor Dauda! Cin Kiritti Te luwe!
\v 12 Wo co yirombo wo ci nekom tiye, kam fiya bweu kumon mor yilango cuwemer, yom mor tokum nennem.
\v 13 Dangjang ri bwe tomange kwama kange mwer kamka dur ko dii kwa'ma caklang kwama ti ciki
\v 14 “Duktanka ki kwama firen dii, rila fuwor nere a fiya tiber nubero co (Kwama) ciyacike.
\v 15 La yilam kambo bi bei tomange kwama dubom ci yilaken dii lo kwamari, nob bi warebbo yi bwiti ci, “na weu ko biya Baitalami nabi to dikero wo bwiyeu, wo Teluwe nung bi neneu”
\v 16 cin cu wulom-wulom wii dila cin fiya Maryamu, Yucufu kange bwe fiyerko dam mor tokume.
\v 17 Kambo ci tom ceri, cin yi nubo dikero cii yi cii dor bwe fiyerko weu.
\v 18 Gwam wo nuwari, ma nyimanka dor dikero nob bi yuwarebbo yi ci yeu.
\v 19 Dila Maryamu ki bulangi dor digero ci nuwa gwam, la cin yoken mor nerece.
\v 20 Nob bi yuwarebo yilaken ci duktangi ri ci caklank kwama ti ki dikero gwam woci nuwau kange wo ci toweu dong-dong nawo ci yi ciyeu.
\v 21 Kambo kume narube dimeri, fiyaco ci biye cinen lareu cin ne co dendo Yecu, dendo bwe tomange kwama ne na nyinde cii tu fwer cereu.
\v 22 Kambo kumeni wucakeu ce cumeri, na wo mor wer fun mucaro, ciin bou ki co bikur waber mor Urucalima naci neken co kwama nin.
\v 23 Nawo mulangum mor werfun Te luwe “Gwam bwe kabo wo bwayileri, atin cokum co ki dimen, cina kwama ce.
\v 24 La cin ma wabka nawo ci toki mor werfun Te luwe re, “nagum fe yob kakaa kalti nawurmero yab”
\v 25 La Nii kange wi Urucalima wu dencero cimon ne, ni wo cak cak laci ne dor bwanka kwama. Ciki ningtan nii a bii Iciraila nin neer tiye, la yuwa kange kwamak wi kange co.
\v 26 La yuwa tangbe kwamako nungcine ki mani ci bwiyati ne citom Kiritti Teeluweri nyinde.
\v 27 La yuwa tangbe kwamako ya ki co mor bi kur waber. Kambo Teb bwe fiyerko Yeco bou kice, naci macinen nawo werfundo nungeu,
\v 28 cin tu beu kangcek ri cin caklang kwama, ciki,
\v 29 na weu dob bwe canga meu akubo ki fuwor neret Teluwa nawo mori tokeu.
\v 30 La nuwe mi tom fuloka mweko,
\v 31 wo mwi yweli nuwe nubo gwammer:
\v 32 filang dukumek wo nubo kumta cili cee kange duktangka wo nubo lomwe Iciraila ce.
\v 33 Tee ce kange nee ce ma nyimankka ki dike ci toki dorce reu.
\v 34 Cimon yocinen bibwiyer, ri yi Maryamu nece ki “Nuwa Yora, bwewo cin co ki na boki yare kange kwenka nubo duce Iciraila na yirome wo ci kowe
\v 35 kange kulen wo abiye ken mor nere mwetiye rila bi kwarum nerem bo kila atim ceruu”.
\v 36 Nawiye tomange kwama ci cuo ti ki Anna wiwi. Cibi bwe Panuel naniya Acar. La cin duyom ki cotini duce, cin yi kange bwece coro kwini niber,
\v 37 la cin nawi ye kwale coro kwini narub-cilombo na'ar. La mani ci dob mor bi kur wabe ri ci wab kwama ki ngak ngake kange dilo kume kange kakuk.
\v 38 Ki kwama co dondong cin kwitau laidom kange ci, ri cin ter buka kau kwama, la cin yi nubo ningtang fuloka Urcalima kotiye ker dor bwero nin.
\v 39 Kambo ci dim digero da ter cin matiye nawo mulangum mor werfun Teluwere di, cin yila keu Galili mor cinanlor ceer Nazaret.
\v 40 La bwen duyom yilam kibi kwan, kange nyomka, la luma kwama wii cinen.
\v 41 Ki cor teb ce bo ki yam nyo Urucalima ki duklume yabka.
\v 42 Ki kwamawo ci dim coro kwabcilom bo yebeu, cin yaken tag duklumenin.
\v 43 La kambo ci diim kumeni duklume gwame ri, cin ter yila kako loweu. La beu Yecu tim ce bwi mor Urucalima ri la teb cebo nyombo.
\v 44 Ci kwotiri ciki no mor mwerka nube kowo ci yaken ti wari yeu. La cin ya yam kume wiine. Di cin ter doka ceko mor naniya cek kange farub cek.
\v 45 Kambo ci fiya ceberi, cin yila ken mor Urucalima la cin ter doka ceko wi.
\v 46 La bwiko kume taare ri cin fiyamco mor bikur waber, yim tiber nob merangkab merangci ke tiniti.
\v 47 La gwam wo nuwa ce ri, ma nyimangka ki nyomka ceko kange ciyaka ceko.
\v 48 Kambo ci toceri, nyimankako tamci, la nee ce yico ki ““ye bwi mwa manyo nye? To, tee mwe kange mo nyi do nen ti ki kwomka duce.” Cin yici, “Ye bwi kom doye tiye? Ko nyombo kambo mamanangen mira?”
\v 49 Con yi ci, ye bwi kom do ye tiye? kom nyomba tam nyo ma nangen Temera?
\v 50 Di ci nyombo dike co yi ti kange kero co toke.
\v 51 La cin yaken lo kange ci mor Nazaret la ci nee ci dur ti. Nee ce yoken diker buro gwam mor nere ce.
\v 52 Dila Yecu ki duwi mor nyomka kange cuwemka la cin fiya cor cini kwama nin kange nob.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Mor coro kwob cilombo nung wo liyar Tibariyuc, la Bilatu Buntu bwangtentiki Yahuda, Hiridu co liya Galili, yice Filibu liya cungako Ituriya kange Tirakonitic, la Licaniyac liya Abiliya,
\v 2 ki kwama Annac kange kayafa nob wabe bo dur keu - ker kwamaro bou Yohana bibwe Zakariya nin mor yere.
\v 3 Cin ya mor bitenni gwam wo cunga caji Urdun ne. Ne fulen ker yika mwenge yilokati na fiya tab ka bwiran kerer.
\v 4 Nawo mulangum mor bi fumer Icaya nii tomange dukumeu, “Diro wo cuo bicor timor yere ko ywelum nure Teluwe, kom tim ki nure ceu ciyer.
\v 5 Bunglunge gwam atim dim, la bangtini gwam kange dukletini atin daken, nureni nyon langi nyeu atin tiken ciyer, fiye bweyang bweyangeu atim twilangum na yilam nure,
\v 6 la nubo gwami auto fuloka kwama”.
\v 7 La Yohanna ji nubo bouti cinen naci yu cinen mwembeu “Kom biwei fangeb! we yi com ki kom cuwa funer wo yautiye?
\v 8 Nyori, kom ne bibeyo wo daten yilaka kumeke, la ko yire dor kimero kom ki “nyin wi tee nye Ibrahim”. La mi yi komti, kwama atin kung Ibrahim nin naniya teren ti wo nin.
\v 9 Wo na weu, biliyeu yom niti tiyer. La tiyo wo nebo bi tuttiyeri atin tom na merken mor kire.
\v 10 Dila nubo ti meka ceko “Ye nya matiye?”
\v 11 Cin ciya cinen ciki, “No kange kume wi ki belle yob ri, ca ti kangum kange nii womancike, wo ki cariyeri a mani nyo ken”.
\v 12 Nob yoka doreb bou ken naci yu cinen mwembo, la cin yi co ki “Nii merangka, ye nyi matiye?
\v 13 Ciin yi ci, “Ko yore kemero a cure dike ci yi kom ko yoweu”
\v 14 Kangem nob kweneb me co ken ki “La nyeu? Ye nyi matiye?” Cin yi ci “Ko yore kemer nii nin kibi kwam ri, ko mwelde nii nin ker ki cuwerke. Ko bulang ki kemer cuwakek kumeko
\v 15 La kambo nubo ningtang bo ka Kiritti tiye ri gwam ce ki kwai mor nere ce dor Yohanna keno co Kritti ri.
\v 16 Yohanna ciya cinen gwam, “Miu, miki yu kumen bwembo ki mwem la kange wi ber wo laye bikwaner, ma labo wo ma kiwi duka ta ceko tiyeu. Ca yu kumen mwembo ki yuwa tangbe kwama kange kira.
\v 17 Kwel yuka ceko kino kang cek na nyinangum tene ceu na mwerken bikate mor bini. La ca tin twim fwirito ki kirako man ki domka”.
\v 18 Ki weranka duce tak, Yohanna yi nubo fulen kerero ken ti.
\v 19 Kambo ci werank Hiru liya ki naka wi yi ceko Hirudiya, kange dikero bwiir tini kangem bo Hiridu maneu.
\v 20 Cin cob ten ki buro gwam, ri cin kum Yohanna fucina.
\v 21 La kambo nubo gwam yum mwem beri, cin yu Yecu nin mwembo ken. La ki kwama ci kwob dilo tiyeri dii kwama wumom,
\v 22 Dila yuwa tangbe kwamako yirau cinen na nagumfe, la diro ceru dii kwama “Mwi bwe nere mii, mi nuwa luma mwek ti?
\v 23 Ki kwamawo Yecu ter nangen cere, can lam coro kwini ta'ar. Cir bi bwe (nawoci kwabi bereu) Yucufu, bi bwe Heli,
\v 24 bi bwe matat, bi bwe Lewi, bi bwe Malaki bi bwe Yanna bi bwe Yucufu.
\v 25 Yucufu bi bwe Mattatiya, bibwe Amoc, bi bwe Nahum, bi bwe Idacli, bibwe Najjaya,
\v 26 bibwe Ma'ata, bibwe Mattatiya, bibwe Climeya bibwe Yoceku, yo ceku bibwe Yoda
\v 27 Yoda bibwe Yowana, bibwe Reca bibwe Zerubbila bibwe Ciyeltiyele, bibwe Niri
\v 28 bibwe Malki, bibwe Addi, bibwe Kocama, bibwe Almadama, bibwe Er,
\v 29 bibwe Yoci, bibwe Aliyeza bibwe Yorima, bibwe Matat, bibwe Lawi,
\v 30 bibwe Caminu, bibwe Yahuda, bibwe Yucufu, bibwe Yohanna, bibwe Aliyakima,
\v 31 bibwe Malaya, bibwe Mainana, bibwe Matata, bibwe Natan, bibwe Dauda,
\v 32 bibwe Yesse, bibwe Obida, bibwe Calmon, bibwe Nacon.
\v 33 bibwe Amminadab, bibwe Adimi, bibwe Arama, bibwe Hezruna, bibwe Feresa, bibwe Yahuda,
\v 34 bibwe Yakubu, bibwe Icaku, bibwe Ibrahim, bibwe Tera, bibwe Nahor,
\v 35 bibwe Cerug, bibwe Reyu, bibwe Feleg, bibwe Abiru, bibwe Cela.
\v 36 bibwe Kainana, bibwe Arfakcada, bibwe Cem, bibwe Nuhu, bibwe Lamek,
\v 37 bibwe Methucela, bibwe Anuhu, bibwe Yaret, bibwe Mahalel, bibwe Kainana,
\v 38 bibwe Enoc, bibwe Citu, bibwe Adamu, bibwe Kwama.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 La Yeecu dim ki Yuwa tangbe kwama, yilam firen caji Urdun la yuwa tangbe kwama ko tu co yakanciko yerak.
\v 2 Fiye kume kwini na'ar bwekelkele cuwaco tiyeu. co ca diker ki kumeni co, la ni connuwa wura.
\v 3 Bwekelkel yii, na mo bibwe kwamri yii tero wo a yilam cari,
\v 4 Yeecu yii co, mulangum mulange “ke bo ka cari ni ama dumetiye”.
\v 5 La bwekelkele kung ken Yeecu dii nung cinen liyaro kaleweu gwam.
\v 6 Bwekelkele yii co, “man neken nen Bikwankero gwam kange duktanka ceko, wori cin neyen dike buri gwam, la man weken nii wo ma cuitiyeu.
\v 7 Na ceu na mwan cung cunge mo wab yeri gwam ka mwe”.
\v 8 La Yeecu karci nen yiico, mulangum mulange mwa wab “Teluwe kwama mwe, co ki kwace mwa- Bwangtentiye”.
\v 9 So bwekelkele yakan ki Yeecu Urucalima, kung ken co diiku'u wabe la yii co na mo bi bwe kwama di yarubitine
\v 10 wori mulangum mulange, can ne be bei tomange wucakke cenin dor mwer bou na cer nen.
\v 11 La ci an kungum nen dii na mo fwere biwure, tero nin.
\v 12 La Yeecu yii co, “tokum toke, mani mwa cuwa Teluwe mwe kwama ti”.
\v 13 La kambo bwekelkele dim cuwa Yeecu keri, concu dubomco biduwar bwiri.
\v 14 La Yeecu yilaken Galili ki kwan yuwa tangber kwamari. La fulen dor ce reu curongi cinanloro kentangum wiye.
\v 15 La can yoten merengkako bi kur waber, La gwam caklang co ti.
\v 16 La con bou Nazaret fiye ci yom co wiyeu la kambo ci lerum maka, con doken mor bi kur waber kakuk folokak, la kwen con titiye na kiye kiye ka ki dir.
\v 17 Cinne co bifumer Nii Dukume kaya, la con fiye wo mulangi,
\v 18 Yuna tangber kwamaka wi dor miri wou cin cor meu timuwang dor na ne fulen kerero ken fiye nob bwen wiyeu. con tuom ye nan kwa dir fiye nubo ci tabangtabangeu, kange nee ka tokak fukmatinimbonin na kwin nubo ci neten dotange tiyeu.
\v 19 Nan kwa dir cor cini kwamar
\v 20 La con cumom bifumer ne riwo timwiyeu. La con yii ken, nuwe nubo gwam bi kur wabero rime ki tokanco.
\v 21 La con yoten kan co yii ci keroti duwen bifumer wo dim fo ki nuwaka kumek.
\v 22 Nubo gwamwi tok kero ken dor cer la citi Nyumangi kange luma kereko ceru ti Nyiceu. La cin me”wo kebo bi bwe Yucufu ka?”
\v 23 La con yii ci, “Bicom kam yii dangke wo kom ki Nii Twaka Twam dor mwero. Dikewo ma duwa ma ma kafarnam meu, ma dong=dong nyo cinan lormwer.
\v 24 La con toki Bicom ma yii komti, nii Dukume kange win wo fiyom bo yoka we cinan lor cer.
\v 25 La mor bilenker ma yii komti, natub kwalebo kila kabo mer Icraila, tiberoco Iliya wiyeu, la biloro mungum na coro ta'areceu kange cuiyakko mukkun, la wura dor bou bitine corin.
\v 26 La ci tun bo Iliya win ciye nin. La tunco Jerefat cidone, nawiye kwale kange yimwiyeu.
\v 27 Walebo kala kabo mor Icraila kwama Ilica nii dukumeu, win wo ci twabo, kan Na'aman wo ciria.
\v 28 Nubo gwam mor bikur wabereu funero tamci kambo cinuwa kero weri.
\v 29 Cin kweri cin cokken co buiko cinan lore ci ya ken kico kong cueli wo ci mum cinan lor ciro dor cereu na ci tungu co bitine.
\v 30 La ca ci cum tiber ciyer co yaken kange fiye.
\v 31 La con yiraken kafarram cinan loro kange mor Galili, la con yoten kange co merang cinenti ki kakuk fobkak.
\v 32 Cin ma nyumanka ki merankaceko, wori co ki tok kero ki Bikwanked.
\v 33 La mor bi ker waber nii kange wi wo ki yuwa kelkelike, la con cii ki dira dur.
\v 34 E' ye nya mam ti ki mo Yeecu Banajara, mo bou na mo twalangum ne? min nyumom mo co nii wucak kwama ce.
\v 35 Yeecu ca kelkeliyomin tor, yii, tok re ker, ceru mor nii wo. kambo kelkeliyo jwa nii wo mer ken bitine tiber ciyer la ce rum mor nii wo, nuwa cinen bo tura ki kange nure.
\v 36 Nubo gwam ti nyumangi, citi tokkami buiti ciye lan ker ye na wo? Co yii kelkeliyo kero ki nyial kange bi kwankered lan cerum.
\v 37 La nyou, cin ter tokka fulen cero cinan loro kantangum wiye gwam.
\v 38 La Yeecu dubom bikur waber ro doken lo cimonne, la fer cimon kalati ki kwirom bwi, la ci ken keri dor cer.
\v 39 La kwen con titye dor cer, co ca kwirum bwi min tor, kwirum buiyo dubomco, dandang con kwemim con ta maka yiroko.
\v 40 Kambo kakuko yar ken tiye ni, rubo bou cinenti kirubo nuwa bo luman tuirako ki dimen ki dimen, con yo ti kang ceko dor ciyer gwam con twam ci.
\v 41 Kelkelibo cerangu mor nubo kila kila ken. Cii wiyeti ci ti toki, “mo bi bwe kwama,” Yeecu ca kelkelibo ca dob ci bo tok ker, wori cin nyumem con co Kritti.
\v 42 Kambo fini celumen con cokum dor ce ki kwace fiye nob mani yeu, nubo ducce docoti co lo ci bou fiye co wiye, cin mani na ci kicim na dob cire.
\v 43 La con yii ci man nee fulen kerer liyar kwamaro tangrim cinan Lorenbo. Won co dike bwi ci tumum ye fe.
\v 44 La con ter neka fuleneko mor bi kur wabero Yuhudiya gwam.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 La yilam kambo nubo mwerum fiye Yeecu wiyeri ci nuwa ker kwamaro, la co tim kang catiyo Janisarat deu.
\v 2 Con to na bire mwenge yo tirangum wi kong caji nin, nubo ta'a jinge cerangum morece nir biliyar ciyer ti.
\v 3 Yeecu kwiken mor Nabire mwengek ro win wuro ki cimonreu, la con yii co a kutaka ten ki nabira mwenge bi dob mor mwenge. La con yii ken mor nabire mwengek ronin, la co merang nubo ninti.
\v 4 Kambo co dim kere di, con yi cimon, kob babire mwenge yaken ciko fiye cuwa cuwau, na mer ken biliyar mwero na taka jinge koce.
\v 5 Cimon yii co “Teluwe, nyo ma nangen kume del nyo taba kange diker wi. La ki ker mwero mamer ken biyaro mor.
\v 6 Kambo ci maweri, ci ta jinge ducce la biliyar ciyero ti biyetangi.
\v 7 Coci ken farub nangeneb ci bo buro nabire mwenge wineu bo na tikanci, cin bou cin dirongum nalire mwengeu ciro yabcite, la cin teri kulkako.
\v 8 La Bitru kambo to Yeecu ri, yarken bitine duwen yeelur la coki, kubom minen, wori min nii Bwiran ke “Teluwe”,
\v 9 wori con nyumami, kange nubo buro kange ceu, ki kilaka jinge ko ci tabe.
\v 10 Wuro mwerum kange Yakubu kange Yuwana bi beyo lo Jabadi farub nangeneb cimaneh. Yeecu yii ciman cuware tai, wori nawo kange kab mwa ta nob.
\v 11 Kambo ci cokum nabire mor mwengecin yoken konge, cin dubom dikero gwam cin buangcinenten.
\v 12 Kambo co ki no win mor cinan lonironineu, kange nii wi dim ki tuirak walek, kambo co to Yeecu ri con yar ken ki tikob ceb la conken co, tokti, “Teluwe” Namo ti ci ri mwantuamye cerum”.
\v 13 La Yeecu ta'ar, kang ce ko keco toki mati cui, yilam wucak, dangjang waleu dubom co.
\v 14 La con yi nii co a yi kange nii, la yii co, ya mure mwe, na nung dor mwero nii waber nin na ne tii kako ficang ngeu. Wo nir mwe ko ceu kambo muca tokeu, na warkero ce cinen.
\v 15 La kero dor cereu yaken ten kutan, la nuba kila kilau bou wari cinen na ci nuwa co ti merangi na twam ten ci twirani ciyeu.
\v 16 La mani co cerum ki kwace co yaken ki kob diloti
\v 17 Yilam win mor kumeniwo co merangkatiyeu faricawa, kange nob merangka wer funer ci yiirongum wi buri ci bourangu muan loro Galili kange Yahudiya kange Urchalima gwam. Bekwan Teluwero wi kange co na co twam.
\v 18 La nubo kange tu kilen do kange dor bilirir, la ci to nure wo ci a dokenti co moreu, na cin yoken co bitine kabum Yeecu.
\v 19 La ci fiyabo nure ci a dor ti ke ceu wori nubo dim kabo, la cin kwiken dor lor la ci cuku co kibi cirico yirau ciko tiber nuber, dong-dong kaa Yeecu.
\v 20 La co to bilenker ciyereri, Yeecu toki nii luwe, cutan mwen bwiran ker mwero wi.
\v 21 Nob mulankabo kange faricawa ter meranka keko wo, we wo tok ker Dila karo wo tiye? we a cutan bwiran keti wi kebo kwama win di?
\v 22 La Yeecu nyam dike ci kwatiyeu, kari yii ci, yebwi ka me wo ti neer kumere?
\v 23 Co wini bwai be na toke, bwiran ke mweu cutang mwenwi, kwen titi ye yayambo.
\v 24 La na kom nyumom bi bwe “Nifire” we ki be kwan kere ro for dor bitininer na cutang biriran ker wi, con yii kilendo, man yii nen kwen, tu bicirimeu, na yaken lomo.
\v 25 Dangjang ko co, co kweri ka bum ciyem la tubiciri ceu wo co dam dor cereu. La cu loco, duktankwama ti.
\v 26 Nubo gwam wi ti Nyumangi, la ci duktang, kwama cin dim ki tai citi toki, loon to diker nyumankar.
\v 27 Kambo dike buro ma nyeri, Yeecu cerum kateb con to ni yo der tiyeu dencero Levi yii ku'u yoka duwek, Lacon yii co bwang menten.
\v 28 Co Levi kwenti bwang cinen ten dubom tangnimdikerenbo gwam
\v 29 La Levi co cika dur loco, la nob yo ka doreko wi kange tangnim nubembo, kentangum fiye caka carikeu ca carito ti kange ci.
\v 30 La fariciwa kange nob mulangekab ciyebo wi fuen bibei tomange ceminti toki, ye bwi ko co ko no kange nob yoka duwek kange nob bwirang kere?
\v 31 Yeecu karci nen, Nubo buro kwamereu mani a do nii Twa ka ti kan co buro nuwa lumau?
\v 32 Ma buobo na nubo dong dongeu, lan nob bwiran kerek na ci yiloten.
\v 33 Cin yii co, bibei tomange Yuwana ki, yim, yim Ngak nyo, ki kuom dilo nyo la bi bei tomange faricawa ki manyo ken. La mweu bi bei tomange meu ti cai ti noi.
\v 34 Yeecu yiici, Nii kange wi wo adok farub bwa yilo na nawite na yii Ngakke, la bwayile na nawiyeu wi kange ci?
\v 35 La kumeni wi bouti wo ci a tum bwayile ti cineneu, la ki kumeni co ci an yii Ngak.
\v 36 La Yeecu yiten ci ker Nyuman kar, nii mani a wor fiti kulenti kulen do fuir na curum carko ciko na co ma nyori, can wobrangum kulendo fuir ko, fiti kulene fuir ko mani a datenti carko nin.
\v 37 La ni kange mani wo a cor ten mwem inabim bo fuir ti mor kole care, naco mani nyo nyori, mwem inabim bo fuir ko an corum koltiye an wuroragum.
\v 38 La tam a cor inabi fuir mor koltinon fuir.
\v 39 Nii kange mani wo nuwa kum mwem inabim bofuir tiye, na kweri con nom car kori. La can toki carko la fuir ko
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 la ma nyo kakuk fobka ko kange, Yeecu yakenti mor to cang ko kange, kange bibei tomange ceu, ci kyang dor canger ti citi kui
\v 2 la kangem mor faricawa tokiki, ye bwi ka ma dike yorbo ti a mani bi diye kukuk, ka kiye for ka?
\v 3 Yeecu kar cinen, toti, ka kiye ba dike Dauda mani kwama co co nuwa wuri ti co kange nubo wari kange ceu?
\v 4 ya mor luwe kwama, con tu cari to tanji laneu ca morece, con nabarubo wari kange ceu ciu cam, bwen no na mam kin nob wabereu ki kwaci cia ca
\v 5 la con yii ci, bibwe nifire co teluwe kankuk fobka ko
\v 6 kange bi diye kakuk fobka con doken mor bi kur waber la co meranmbo minti wi, nii kange wi wi wuro kance ko catiyero bwiyam-bwiya
\v 7 nob mulangkabo kange faricawa to co tibi dor kero can twa nii ni kakuk fobkari na cin fiyan mure wo ci a tamco tiyeu,
\v 8 la con nyumom dike ci kwa tiyeu la con yii nii wo kangko bwiyame kwen ti fo tiber nubero gwam la nii wo kweni titi wi.
\v 9 Yeecu me ci yori kebo bi diye kakuk fobka a dike yor yoreu, kaka a ma dike wo yorbeu a cok dume kaka a tual dume?
\v 10 la con cto ci gwam la co yii nii wo yarken kangmweko, la con manyo, la kang cebo twam
\v 11 la neer ciyero kayaragum, lacin tok kanti bwiti ciye dike ca ma Yeecu nin tiyeu
\v 12 lan yilam mor kumeni wo con ceri con yaken bang ca kob dilo con ta kobka dilo kume del co ken kwama ti
\v 13 ki kakuk la con co bibei tomange ceu cinen la con cokum kwob cilom bo yobeu, wo co co cibitikali,
\v 14 denti bi beitomange ceu co buro cimon [wo co caten tak, Bitru ] kange yii Andrawu, Yakubu, Yuwawana, Filibu, Bartalomi,
\v 15 Matta, Toma, Yakubu bibwe Afa, cimon wo ca co Jaloti
\v 16 Yafuja, bi bwe Yakubu, kange Yafuja ckaryoti wo miye co tiyeu,
\v 17 la Yeecu yirau dor banged kange ci laci tim fiye tuared deu, kange bi bwi tomange ce wila kange nubo kila wo borongu Yafudiya kange wurcalima kange nubo kong caji taya
\v 18 ci bou na ci buro wo nuwa co na co twam twirani ciyeu, nubo buro nuwa dotange ti ki yuwa kelkelikeu con twam ci ken.
\v 19 nubo mwerkangum we gwameu dotina ci kem co wori bikwan twa ka ro ceru ti cinen, la con twan ci gwam.
\v 20 la con to bi bei tomangeceu. con yii ci bibuyer kume kom wo nob bune beu la na kume liyar kwamaro
\v 21 bi buyero an kume, kom wo konuwa wurati naweu, la ci an bwa kumen fuer bibuyer na kume, kom wo ko ci wiye tina weu, la kan nung nungi
\v 22 bibuyero na kume to kom la ci ko denkumero na dikero bwir, ki ker bi bwe nir
\v 23 ko bilangi diye co ko yilam ki for neerer, wori kan fiya cuner dikwama nubo carem cim ma nob du kumebo nin nawo
\v 24 la kwan nen mo nii mwa cuwe-cuweu, la mom yom mwe dangne mweu
\v 25 kwan kom nubo wo fuero bwam bwabeu, kan ci wura for kob kwan kom wo ko nung nungi ti na weu, yii kan buwa kan ci wiye ki bui.
\v 26 kwan kom na nubo tok ti ki wo dong dong di, nubo carem cimbo tok nyo nob dukumeb cwerkebo
\v 27 la ma yii komti nubo ko nuwa ye tiyeu, cui nii bi dom kange mweu, na ma nubo konene nin dike ro ken
\v 28 yo nubo cilnen tiye nin bibuyer, na kob nubo buro culong nen ti dor bilenkereu
\v 29 wo na kwanen ki kang tangal do wineri, neco wineu na kange tum belle mweri tamde mwe
\v 30 ne nuwa wuro meneneu gwam na kange tum dike kangen na mweri me core moki a bou mwen ciko
\v 31 kambo mo cuilti nubo a ma mweneri, mo keneu ma ci nen nyo
\v 32 na moki cuim ka co ka co nubo cuinen tiyeri, in jye yokka fiye mo wiye? bwen na nob bwirang kerer di cui nubo cui ci tiyeu.
\v 33 na moki mam dikero ken kan co nubo ma mwen dikero ken tiyeri ye yokka fiye weye? bwen no nob bwirang keri ki mam nyo ken
\v 34 na wo ki ne cen kan nubo mo totiri an yam neneri, ye yokka munen? bwen no nob buiran kerer di ki nem nob bwiram kerero nyou na ci fiya dike ci ne dng-dong
\v 35 la cui koneneu, na ma cinen dike dong-dong ngeu. ne ken kware kange diker yilau ti, la cuner, kumero na dur, kan yilam bi beyo lo nii dii ko na co con ni lomjome fiye nubo man ki buka kangek kange nubo bwirko
\v 36 yilam ki cini na wo tee kume nii ciniu
\v 37 kom mare buolang la mani a ma kumen buolang ti kom kuwa re mani a kuwa komti, tab kangem bo la mweu an tab mwen
\v 38 kom ne la an ne kom kwele dimdiye, cuwam cuwa, ki bi funger ti con ci an cor kumer ti kan bellik ki kwele ka cuwameu a cuwa kumen ciko
\v 39 la yila con yii ten ci dangke kange, con toki, fukma an ta fukma nin kangka? na co ma nyon, yaramken buwar gwam citi cimanin nyoka?
\v 40 bwe tomange labo nii merang ka ceu dur la nubo gwam an yilam na nii merang kako na merang cinendi
\v 41 ye bwi mo toti ka be yere nuwa kemwe, lamwa tobo cuwemero wo nuwe mweu
\v 42 mwa yii yimwe myi, moki yii mi tumwen be yere dam mor nuweu, lamoki bwi mwa tobo kukko cuwe mero dam mor nuwe mweu? kom nubo bwir, teri cokum batiye durko nuwe mweu na mo tom yora na mo cokum be yere nuwe yiim weu
\v 43 la tiyo kendo kange mani wo tu bi tutiyo fuyem fuye tiye, kaka tiyo wo fuyemeu na ne betuti ken
\v 44 wori tiyo moki nyomco kin bitutico tutiyeu la nubo mani we bituti nying cire ti cuiya ke kaka nubo inabi fiye cilange
\v 45 nii ken mor dikero kendo dume ceu a bou dikero yor yoreu, nyou nii bwirko mor dikero bwirko mor neere ceu, a bou dikero bwir wori dikero bwirko ducce mor neere ceu co ci ceu toktiye
\v 46 ye bwikaco yeti kom ki, teluwe laka bwantenbo dike ma tok tiyeu?
\v 47 nii wo na bou minen la nuwa ker mereu laco bwang tenen, man yii dii ke co cerkange
\v 48 co ki no nan nii luwe tiye, woru wobken cuwa mor bitinen la co mu kwar loro ki terenti kwamer lana mwembo dur bouri la came mwegweu kwanan kwar kumeroti laluwe cuwo mani a muka ti wori mum co yora
\v 49 la nii nuwa ker miro bwang ten beu no nan co nii wo mu luwe dor bitinereu man ki kwar ca na came mwem bo kwanan kwar kuro di la can can duwo an yarum, yarke luwe kowo
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 bwiko Yeecu dim dikero gwam ca yi nobo tiye cin do ken kafarnaum
\v 2 fiya cuwo nii kwene durko nuwa diker dor Yeecu ri, contwom nobo dur yahudawa ro, a ken co na bou na twam canga ceu
\v 3 la cin bou Yeecu nin cin ken co yi co ti ki “nii wo lam wo ma macinen wo tiye
\v 4 wori ci cwi bitene nye ti co ca munyinen bi kur kwamaro urcalimau
\v 5 nyori Yeecu bwan cinen ten. la fiya cuwo ci dadom kange kuweri, nii kwene durko twom farub cebo a yi co, teluwe kwom de dor mwero, wori ma labo wo mwabouti lomiyeu
\v 6 nyori ma tubo dor miro na nii wo lami mwa bouti cinen, tok ka ker koni, canga mi an kwam.
\v 7 mo keneu, mi nii woki bi kwang kere dor nob kwenebo kang mikeu, nyi wo mi yari, co ya kange mi bouri, co bou, canga miu no ca ma wori can mani
\v 8 la Yeecu nuwa wori, co nyiman nii wo, con yila nobo bwan cinententiye, con yii ci, “miyi komti, mor kiraila gwam, ma fiyobo nii ki bilen ke na weu.
\v 9 fiya cuwo nobo ca twome a yilaure loweri, ci fiya canga wo twam
\v 10 kutanbo bwiko cuwori
\v 11 Yeecu yaken cinar loro kange ci cuwoti ki Naim, nob tomange cebo fiya nob ducce woya kange ceu
\v 12 la ci bi dom kangenyilo cinar loreu di, cin ki nii kange wo bwiyam meu, cobwe wiin nece nin [wuro] nawiye kwale nubo ducce cinar loron wo kange co.
\v 13 Yeecu to cori, cin bunang co cin yii co, “ciire wiye”
\v 14 la conyaa con tei kwanni wo ci tuu bilen do cika nobo tum ki bilen nen tim cok con yico, bwe, mi kwenu”
\v 15 bilen do kwenum, nyoten tok ka kereko, Yeecu neken co nece nin
\v 16 la tai to tam ci gwam, cin yoten ci caklang kwama ti,” nii tomange kwama dur kwennu more nye kwama to nobo loceu
\v 17 fulen kere wo dor Yeecu yalti bi ten yahudiya gwam kange buro bi dom kange ceu
\v 18 bibei tomange yuwana yi co dike buro gwam
\v 19 la yuwana cuwo bi bei tomange ce yob, tom ciYeecu nin ciya me co” mo nii bou tiye kakaa nyo nintang kane?
\v 20 cin bo bidom Yeecu nin di cin toki, “yuwana nii yuu mwem tiye tom nyo munen ki nyi me, “mo wo bou tiye kakaa nyi nintang kange?”
\v 21 tabbo cin twabangum nubo ki twira kange wo ki yuwa kelkeleb beu, nobon fukmau, cin neci toka fiye.”
\v 22 la Yeecu ciya cinen ki, kom ya ko yi yuwana, dike nuwa kime towe kange dike ka nuwa fukma tofiyeti kilendo ya yamti, walebbo cin twam, nubo mani nuwa tiye ti nuwai, nobo bwiyame kwennum, fuwabbo nuwa fulen keret
\v 23 nii wo ne bilen keret dikero mi matiyeri nii bibwiyer,
\v 24 bwiko bi bei tomange yuwana cuwe, Yeecu yici kerdor yuwana,”ye ka crr yera ka totiye? yerayuwana moktiye ka
\v 25 ye ka cer yera ka owe? nii ki kulendo twaba nyeu to, nubo ki kulenkyemereu, ci nuwa lima ti loni liyabe
\v 26 ye ka ya yera ka towe? nii tomange kwama ong mi yi komti la nii tomange
\v 27 wuro co nii ci mulangi cer ki “to mi tom mweu ni tomange ti kaa mo wo a ywelmwen nuretiye
\v 28 mi yi komti mor nubo natub bowe, mani na yuwana, nyori nii wo na bi duware mor liyar kwama reu laco
\v 29 la nubo gwam, ki nob yuwana kyemerek nuwa nyori, cin ciya kwama nii wucake, wori cin yuu cinenen mwembo ki yuu mwemer yuwana
\v 30 la fariciyawa kange nubo nyimom werfundeu cin dike kwama yo keb dor circu, nyori ci yuu cinen bo mwem yuwanam bo tiye? cinan ye?
\v 31 “kange ye ma mwer nubo kaldo wo canne tiye? cinanye?
\v 32 cina bi bei malorti fiye miyeka dikereu, wo yim yiye la cuwo kange yi co ki,”min cuu lira mwa yelbo yila, min ka nuwe bware, mwa cibo wiye
\v 33 nyo yuwana nii yuu mwem tiye bou mani cati, mani noti, ki wi ki ninga “
\v 34 bi bwe nifire bou, ti cai ti noi ri, kom ki kucunu kange nii no nyom tiye, farnob yuwana kyeme kange nii ki bwiran kere,
\v 35 nyore yuleng bi beyo loce ki warke
\v 36 na wori, wiin mor fariciyawa cuwo Yeecu na ci ca cari wari la bwiko Yeecu doken lon fariciyawari, cin yiken fiye caka carik, na cincam cartori,
\v 37 nawiye kange wii cinar lor wo nii bwiran ke kambo cin nyimom Yeecu doken loh bwe fariciyawa ca kacarik di, cin bou ki nuwan alabata, kundo limi yeu
\v 38 contibidom kange Yeecu fiye na ceko wiye co ci wiyeti, con yoten yibong na Yeecu ko ti ki mwem num cem, belti nuwang na cek
\v 39 la fariciyawa wo cuwo Yeecu, to nyori, co ti kwabi ner cer ki, na nii wo bwe tomange ri no cikin nyimom we nawiye tiye nii bwiran ke'
\v 40 Yeecu yi co cmon min wi dike ma yi nen tiye, ciki toki nii meranka
\v 41 Yeecu ki nii neka cennek ne nubo yob cend, wiindinari kwini kwob nung, wiineu nung
\v 42 la cin fwe ki yakako, cin dobcinen gwam nyori we more ciye co cwiti wo ducce?
\v 43 ciman ciya ki, “mi kwatiri nii wo co dob cin kyemero ducceu. Yeecu yico co ki munwarker dong-dong
\v 44 Yeecu yila nawiye wonin yi ciman, mun to nuwiye wamin do lomo, mwe ne yebo mwem nirka nam, na wiye wo yibong namiko mwem num ceu, con ki yiri co
\v 45 mwa ma membo ka cikko ma dou feu na wiye wo dobbo beitika na miko
\v 46 mwa beltimen bo nuwandor, nawiye belti menti nuwan dor
\v 47 nyori mi yinenti bwiran kece ducceu cutan wi, wori con nan cwikaducce nii wo cicutan bwiran kece bi duware ri, cwika ceko bi duwar
\v 48 la con,” yi co, bwiran kemwe cin cutang wi
\v 49 nubo ci yim wariyeu yotan tokkan kerek butici, we woro cutan bwiran ke tiye
\v 50 Yeecu yi nawiye wo, bilenke mwe coknen, ya ki nero fwor
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 la yilam nyo kambo Yeecu ter yam cembo cinar lor kange mwanti lore ki kang ki wang, tok fulen kereroti kange fulen liyar kwama kwob culombo yobeu wi kange co,
\v 2 kange natubo kange wo ca twam ci yuwako kwir kange twira kila-kila. maryamu wo ci cuwo ti ki makdaliya, wo ci cokten ninga nibereu,
\v 3 kange yuwana wii kuza, nawiye tomange hiridu, cuzanatu, kange kangumbo kila nyeu, kin dike kang cike ci ma mangen ti cikr
\v 4 la nubo ducce mwekangu ti, kange kangum nob bouti cinar lor-cinar lor reu, cin yii ci dangke,
\v 5 nii fike kange ciri a fii dum la coti fii ri kangum bo yarken kong nure, cin fawarangum ki na, bilibeu diyeu yirau bon com.
\v 6 kangumbo yar dor terenti, la kii ri kucom, dula mani
\v 7 kangumbo yarken mor cwiyaka la cwiyak kii kange dumbo ri, cwiyakko cakkangum co
\v 8 la kangumbo yar bitine kenneu ma ken, wo lam kiriti kwini kwobbe. bwiko Yeecu dim tokka kere keu, cuwo ci, “ki tu nuwaka kere, ca nuwa
\v 9 bi bei tomange ce meco dang kewo nuntiye con yici, la kangum bo ciye me yici ki dangka, nyori ci ti toi maci toti citi nuwai ma ci nyomti
\v 10 con yici, nyomka yurke liyar kwamar cin nekom, la kangum bo ciye ma yi ci ki dangka, nyomti
\v 11 dike dangka nuntiyeu co wo, dumbo ker kwamar
\v 12 buro yar nureu, wori nuwa ri bwekelkele bou yuwom kero ner cireu, nyo na ci nere bilenke naci fiya fuloka
\v 13 buro yar do terentiyeu, co buro no ci nuwa kero dici yuwo ki nero for, la ci man ki niti, cin ne bilenke, kutan bori, cuwakako bou ri ci yarum.
\v 14 dumbo wo yar mor cwiyakeu, ci nobo wo nuwa ri, la ci yakenti ri, cwika kalek, kyemer kange nuwaka lima ca kkangum ci la ci mabo ken
\v 15 woro dor bitinero keneu, ci buro ki bilnka kange nero kenne, tam yoran, ma dikero ken mor birum nere.
\v 16 nii mani a kwer kirati na cumom, kakaa yoken bok kwannik, ca yo codor diker, na nobo doutiye to kirako
\v 17 mani dikero yurangum yurange mani a nyomtiye, kakaa yurke kange wii wo ba nyombe a bou ti kira
\v 18 nyori nuwa, yora, nii wo ki diker ducceu ri an yok cinen ten woro man cikeu, bi duwar ci cikeu an yuwom cinen.
\v 19 la nece kange yitub ceb bou, cinen, la ma ciya fiya nure lakati cinen, wori nubo ducce
\v 20 cin yi co, nemwe kange yitub mwem tim kale, cwiti na ci tonen”
\v 21 Yeecu ciya ci yi ci, nemi kange yitub mib co nobo wuro nuwa ker kwama di ma namgen cike.
\v 22 bi con doken mor nabire mweme kange be bei tomange ce, con ci,”bi yabken dinge wure no cin yoten yambo,
\v 23 la ciyakentiri, co dam dum yuwa kibi kwama kwennuncayi, mwembo yoten dim na bire mwenge ciyeuti, ciki no nyi kware.
\v 24 la bi bei tomange Yeecu bou cinen cin yunco, ciki “teluwe, nyo nyi bware con kweni, yuwako kange mwelanka mwemek ko, wori cin tim
\v 25 la con yi ci ki fe ke kimeu? cin nuwa tai ci myimam dike woti ci me buti citi we nii wuro werang yuwati kange mwembo ki nyial neco dure?
\v 26 la cin yaken Garacinawa wo kino dinge caji Galili
\v 27 fiya cuwo Yeecu doken bitene, cowari, con wabkan nii kange cerum cinar loreu ki ninga kwutangi cinen la wormangum kulen cero. mani dã lo ki dã tiber tuwetini
\v 28 la con Yeecu ri con kwa dir yarkan ka Yeecu, cin tok ker kwang ka, ki mo Yeecu bi bwe kwama nii duktonka, mi kennenti neyere dotange
\v 29 wori Yeecu cokkan yuwakeliko ki nyial nii cuwo nin kiritti ducce ki ta core bwentano cin bwam cori cin yoti nii atocotiri, kiyangum diker bwakaro, ningau ywa co yaken ciko yera
\v 30 la Yeecu me co, “we den mwero? ki dencero muri, wori kelkelibo ducce do bwiciye
\v 31 ci ken Yeecu ti a ywa cire ki nyial mor buwoke
\v 32 na wen, ngiyere ducce ca cariti fir banger ninga buro ken co ca dob ci ciya doken bwi ceru la cin ne ci nure
\v 33 nyori ninga buro ceru bwi nii wuro doranken bwi ngiyere tini cin cwakkangi yaranken mor mweme cin bwiyarangum
\v 34 la nubo to ngiyere buro tiye, dike wo mane ri, cin cwakkan ken mor cinar lor cin yi nubo dikewo bwiyeu
\v 35 la nubo cecu naci to dikero maneu, cin bou Yeecu nin, cin fiya nii wo cokten ningau yim bi dom na Yeecu, dumki kulen, wo kwamer tak. lacin cwa tai
\v 36 la nubo to dikero maneu, yi dike maneu, yuwa kelkelibo wo cerum bwi nii we
\v 37 la nubo gwam biten Garacinawau yi Yeecu a dobom bitine ciyeu wori taito dur tamci nyori cin doken nabire mwenge naci yilaken bwi.
\v 38 nii woci cokten ningau ken Yeecu na cin ya wari, la Yeecu yi co,
\v 39 yilaken lo na yii nubo dike kwama ma cineneu nii woro kentangum cinar loro gwam, tok dike Yeecu ma cinenu
\v 40 na weu Yeecu yilaken neu nubo duccu nawo yuwoce, no ci nintang coti
\v 41 la nikange wi dendo ki Yariyu, ciki no mor nubo durer kwamaro Urcalima, bou bidom kange Yeecu cungen naa Yeecu, con ken co ca ya loco,
\v 42 wori, bi bwece bwebubya, coro kwob culombo yob, kan co wiin cineneu ki no nyi kware laYeecu yaken tiri nubo ducce tunkanti bwiti ciye kentangum co
\v 43 la nawiye kange wo cor gwam dike ci cikeu bwiyale ti coro kwob culomo yobe, twalum gwam dike ci cikeu, co fiyabo twaka nii kange nin
\v 44 co bou bwi Yeecu con tei nyii belliceu, wii dancan kwiyele ceu tim.
\v 45 la Yeecu yiki we kece? la nii wo ciya cinen wii more ciye gwam di, bituru yi co, nii merangka, nubo duccu kantangum mo, tunkanti bwimi
\v 46 Yeecu yi co “kange nii ke ye, min yimom, bikwan ceri minen.
\v 47 na wiye wo to nyo ma ca fiye cerka ti ri con bou fiye Yeecu wiye, cungi kaco, nuwe nube gwan, con tok ca fiya dikero gwam wo dok co ca ke ce, la nyoro, ca kfiya twaka
\v 48 la con yi co, “bwe, bilenke mwam nen, yaa ki for nerek
\v 49 con wi co tok ker ti duwal di kange bou bi kur kwama nubo dure, ki bi bwe mwe bwiyam, ki nere ni meranka dotange tak
\v 50 Yeecu nuwa wori, con ciya yariyu nin nuwari tai neka bilenke, bi bwemwe atwam
\v 51 la ca ya luwe cori ca dobbo nii a do mor kange co kange Bitru kange Yuwana kange Yakubu te kange ne bweu
\v 52 nubo wiye ci ti wori bweu bwiyami la con yi ci kom cire wiye co bwiyabo, ki dadum
\v 53 la cin mung co, wori cin nyimom bwiyam
\v 54 co tu bwe kang cer, cin cuwo ki bi kwang bwenu yi ci ciya fiya cinen dike ca catiye
\v 55 dume ce yilaken, dancan con kwenu con yi ci ciya fiya cinen dike ca catiye
\v 56 teekange nece nyimangi, con yici ciya yi re nii dike wo maneu.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 con cuwo bi bei tomange ce kwob culombo yob, neci bikwang kange bikwang keret naci cokum ningga gwam, ci twam tiratini
\v 2 con twom ci kele na ci tok fulen keret liyar kwamaro, naci twam nubo nuwabo liman
\v 3 con yi ci kom ture diker yam kimembo nin dang mani cwaye mani, cari mani, kyemer mani tak ko ture diker kwabkar yob
\v 4 luwe wo ka dowe ri, ko yi wii yaken ciko diye ka dubom tiye
\v 5 fiye ci yuwo kom be ri no ka dob ninar loro cuwo tiri ko bum kwero na kime keu warke dor cir
\v 6 nyori cin kweni, ci bwanten cung-nukur, cunkur ci tok fulen kerero ti, twa nob ti fiye gwam
\v 7 la Hiridus liyau nuwa dike ydken tiye ri, ma nyimantum, wori kangum bo tiki kin Yuwana kwenu bware
\v 8 kangum bo ki Iliya cerkangu we, kangum tak ki wiin more nob tomangeb bo fiya cuwo kutaneu kwenuwe
\v 9 Hiridu ki, min mwatum dor Yuwanaro, we wori mi nuwa dikero woti dor cere? nyori con do nure ca to co tiye
\v 10 la be bei tomange Yeecu yilauri, cin co dikero gwam ci maneu la con cin yaken yurangum, yurange cinar loro ci cuwo tiki Batsaidau
\v 11 la nubo mwerumem nuwa dike wuro nyori cin bwangten co con yuwo ci, con ci diker dor liyar kwamare, com twam buro cwi twaka tiyeu
\v 12 lakume dadom a bouti cwile, kwob culombo yobe bou cinen, cin yico,”yi noboro ci yaken mwan loro buro mor tangini naci fiya fiye dame kange cari nyori fiye biwiye nob mani
\v 13 la con yi ci, “ko neci dike ciya ca tiye. ciki, be dike nyo cikeu cwen carito nug kange jinge yob ma nya fiye carito wo a lam nubo wuro ti gwame
\v 14 nubo lam bikate nung ka nabarub con yi bi bei tomange ceu ki yi nubo a yiken ki mwam, kimwam nubo kwini nung, kwini nung
\v 15 nyori cin mani nyo, yo nubo yiken yiye
\v 16 co n tu cwen tiyero nungeu nunge jinge yobe, cin kunken nuwe ce di kwama, yo cin nenti bi bwiyer wi con wulangum ka bi duwartini con ne bi bei tomange ceu naci tikange nubo mwerume nin
\v 17 cin ca gwam ciye cin bwam, tanne ceu numeu, cin yee bulendo kwob culombo yob
\v 18 la kakuko kange Yeecu kwob diloti ki kwace, bi bei tomange ce wi cinen con me ci ki nubo wuro mweru meu ki yii ki min wee?
\v 19 cin ciya co yuwana nii yuu mwem tiye, kangumbo ki Iliya, la kanugumbo ki kange wiin mor nob tomangebo nanduwe
\v 20 con me ci la kime kom ki yi ki min wee? Bitru ciya cinen kiritti bi bwe kwama
\v 21 cin werang ci ciya tok re wo nikange nin
\v 22 yi citi bi bwe nifire an nuwa dotange dike ducce, ko co, ci an twalum co, ki bi kume taare an kwenum
\v 23 con yi ci gwam, nii wo cwiti na bwanten yereu, an ko dor cero, can tun bentilen bwantiyer ki cero, ki ca kicatecca bwan teng
\v 24 ni wo cwiti na ci fiya dume ce ri an lem dume ce, wo lem dume ce ki 25ker mire ri an fiya dume ceu
\v 25 yee nii a fiya tiye no ci fiyam kale wo gwam la co lem dume ceri
\v 26 wo no nuwa kwenduwe mi kange ker mirro ri, bi bwe nifire an nuwa kwenduwe ce ken diye bi bwe nifire a bou ti mor dukfongka ce, duktongka tee, kange yuwa tangbe kwama wucake
\v 27 mi yikom bilen ke ti, kangembo wii tirangum fo, wo mani a twi bwer tiye nimre ci to liyar kwamaro
\v 28 ki kume narub Yeecu tok kero bure ri, cin tuu Bitru, kange Yuwana kange Yakubu, cin kukendor banger na ci kwobdilo
\v 29 la ci mor kwobka dilo ri, tikob ce bo fulongum, kulen cere yilam fwoje ti milbangi
\v 30 nyori, nubo kange yob tokkang ker ti kange co, muca kange Iliya,
\v 31 wo cerkengu ki duktonka, tokkan ker kiboka cer ti wom dadom a bou ti cwile urcalima
\v 32 Bitru kange buro kange ceu nuwe ciye tuu ki dum, la cin kweni ri, ci to duktonka kange nobo yob tim kange co
\v 33 fiya cuwo ci dob Yeecu ci yakentiri, Bitru yi co teluwe yor nyinen nyi feu, bi ywel bikur taar, wiin ki mo wiin ki muca, wiin ki Iliya [co nyombo dike co tok tiye ]
\v 34 la co tok kero ti nyori, bi loro yirau cumom ci, cin nuwa tai kambo bilora kantangum ciyeu.
\v 35 diro kange ceru mor bilore nin ti toki ki, wo bi kwemi ma cikeu, ko nuwa co
\v 36 fiya cuwo diro dim tokka kere keu, Yeecu tim ki kwace la cin kumom ci yi bo nii mor kumeni curo dike ci towe
\v 37 cel fini ri cin yirau dor banger, nobo duccu bou cinen
\v 38 wori nikange mor nibe nin cuwo co ki diri, nii merangka, mi cwiti na to be bweme kange co bweu mi cike
\v 39 yuwa tangbe bwir doken bwici, co ki kwa kang kiyange, mok co ti kibi kwang, funi fwiuti nyii co, bwai na dob co, nuwaran cinen twira ti bwira-bwira
\v 40 min ken be bei tomange na cokum, cin fwe ciko
\v 41 kom kaldo woka tiyangum nure, kom man ki bilen kereu, fiyan ma yiti kange kome, mi mwirimum ner ti kange kome? bou kibi bwe mwe fo
\v 42 la bwe bou boutiri ninga kwa co merken bitine, mor coti kibi kwang Yeecu werang yuwa tangbe ko wo, con twam bweu yila cin neken tece
\v 43 nubo nyimang bi kwan kwamaro laci tokkanti butici dikero gwamco matiye, con yi bi bei tomange ceu,
\v 44 kom dor kero wo a yiraken tuu komi ciyang miyem bi bwe nifire kang nubek
\v 45 la ci nyombo dike co tokeu, yurangum, yurage cinen, laci nyombo dike nuntiye, ci cwa tai ti na ci me co kerowo
\v 46 kwobokanka do tiber ciyer ki kerowo kin we a yila nii dur tiye.
\v 47 Yeecu nyimom dike ci kwati ner cireu, tuub bwe bi duware bi dom kange co.
\v 48 la con yi ci, niwo yuwo bwe bi duware ki den mire ri, yuwo mo, na wo yuwo yere yi, yuwo niwo tomu yereu nii wo bi duwar more kume gwamme co durko
\v 49 Yuwana ciya co, teluwe, nyon to nikange cok ninga ti ki den mwer, co nya ywace wori bwang nyinen ten bo.
\v 50 Yeecu yi ki, ko ywa core, wori nii wo ciya kombe na kume
\v 51 la kumeni kum bi duwar wo ci yilaken diye, con yoken ner yamer urcalima
\v 52 con twom bi bei tomange na yaken ten cinnen, cin ya cin doken mwan lor camariyar na ci ywel cinen fiye firen
\v 53 nii bo wiye yuwo cobo wori ciki yang urcalima
\v 54 la bi bei tomange ceu Yakub kange Yuwana to nyori yi ki, “teluwe muki cwi nyo dor kirako a yirau di kwama na twim ci ka?
\v 55 con yila con werang ci,
\v 56 la ci yaken mwam luwero kange
\v 57 ci mor yamme dor nuret, kange. yii co, “mwan bwang mwen ten fiye mo yaken ti wii ye
\v 58 Yeecu yi co, “bi cwe kiye wiki buokti, bi libe di kwama wii ki loci, la bi bwe nifire man ki fiye ca nyom dor tiye
\v 59 la cin yui kange, “bwangmen ten, la con yi co ki, “teluwe dob ye yan fwerum temi buri”
\v 60 cin yi co, dob bilendo cika fwerum bilen ciyer mweu ya kutan kange fiye kwiya kye na tok fulen liyar kwama.
\v 61 dila kange yi ki man bwanten nen kwama dila dob ye yan nem nubo lomembo nanme”
\v 62 Yeecu yi co, ni kange mani a yoton kanti cinonri la yi la yila nuwe bwiye daten bo lokwama.
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 Bwika dike wuro Yeecu cok kwini niber cilom yoh, co tom ci yob-yob na ci ya cunnukur kange bettinimbo wo co cwija. Ya ka ti wiyeu.
\v 2 La yi ci bituwe wi dutce di la nob nangnembo biduwa, no nyori kom kwob dilo kom kinong nii take na tom cimen nob nangenembo mor take ce.
\v 3 Kom ya to man tom kom na be kwame mor bitilo.
\v 4 Be kom ture kiyemer, cwaye kange Taa. kom yarumde nii dor nuret.
\v 5 Luwe kom do wiyeudi, kom ter tok kako kom ki, funeret a no fo luwe wuro.
\v 6 Tano ni funeret wi luwe nen di, fu neret kumero an yiti luwe nen, no mani dii fowor neret kumero an yila fiya kom.
\v 7 Kom yi i luwe co, kom ca kom no, dike ci ne kome. Ni nage do daten cor cero, kom dore luwe-luwe.
\v 8 Bero ci yo komeri kom ca diker ci ti ki kabum kumene.
\v 9 Kom twam nubo ki bwarakeu wii bitine cuwo, kom yici liyar kwamaro bo bi dom kange kom.
\v 10 Bitine wo kom do no ci yokom di yaken dor nuret ciyer, kom yi nubo cuwo kom kii ka kwero bitine kume tam na nye ko.
\v 11 Nyo ferkumen, co warke dor kumer. Be kom nyom liyar kwamaro bo bi dom kange kom.
\v 12 Ma yi kom bi diye bolange caduma an la bero wo, fiyaka luma.
\v 13 Kwannen karacinu, kwannen Baitcaida: nangedo tenangi wo ma mo re kume, na cin mani nyo Taya knge cidon di na cikin kiya ciko ki kinin, ci yim mor bituwamekange yilan kangbuwa.
\v 14 Di la biye bolang taya kange cidon ci an La kom fiya ka luma.
\v 15 Mo kenne kafanaum mo kwati moki yaken ciko dii kwama ciya duktang nen tiye? O-ong an cukken nen bwiyar.
\v 16 Wuro cutu fiye kom wiyedi, cuwantu minen, wo ko kom medi, koye, wo ko yere, ko niwo tomwo yere”.
\v 17 Ci kwini ibere yilau ki fwor neret, ci yiti ki Teluwe, bwekelkele ken nyo durti. mor denen mwe?
\v 18 La Yeeecu yici man to bwekelkele yaruti dii kwama na miblanka.
\v 19 To min ne kom bi kwan kom fuwa na cwiwetininm kange birngetinim kange bikwan nii kiyer gwam, take ci makom nin ki diger ko bi dob.
\v 20 Bwen nyeu kom bilangde nyo kom ki yuwa ko bwirko nuwa komti, Di la kom bilangi la den kumer mulangum mor dii kwama.
\v 21 Na wo ri Yeecu dim ki for neret mor yuwa tangbe ko wucakke, coki man ne nen dur Te Teluwe dii kwama kange bitine. wo mo cumom dige worombo nob Yilenebbo nin kange nyomka, mo na fwetang ci nen nubo worombonin merangbe. na bibei bi dwartinim. Ong, Tee nyo dong dong fiye mon wiyeu.
\v 22 Dikero gwam ki no fiye Tee me wiyeu, ba nii win nyom bwe curoweu, La ka Tee win kange kangumbo wo bwe ciya ki nyomom ceu.
\v 23 La cin yilam fiye bibei tomangeb cebo con cogi cunnka. Caklangka ki no nubo wo tom dikere cin toweu.
\v 24 Min yii komti nub wabero kange liyab kila ciyan to diker muu toweu, la ma ci to cii ti, ciyan nuwa diker muu nuwau, la ma ciya nuwati
\v 25 Kange nii merangka bolange Yahudawa na co cwa co, cike na co cuwa co, cike nii meranka, Yeecu ma matiye na fiyam dume diiye?
\v 26 Yeecu yi co ki moki kiye nyi dike mulangi mor bolange? co ciya coki.
\v 27 Bilang te mwe kwama ki ner mwero gwam, dume mwe gwam, bikwan mwer gam, kange dike mo kwabe gwam, na mo bilang nii bidomeu na dor mwero.”
\v 28 Yeecu ciya co mo tok dong dong, ma wo nyo na fulo
\v 29 Nii merang ka cwiti na co cukum dorcero, ki Yeecu we nii mi bidome?
\v 30 Yeecu ki nii kange kwen yam Ursalima, yakenti Jeriko. Con yar ken kan nub kwiyeb, ci cukum co, ci yom dike co cike kwarub ci bukco dob co tamwi bwiyam.
\v 31 Nii wabe kange dou wi nure co, to co di kwen tiyagum cungagin cuken.
\v 32 Nyo tak ni tikali dur bikur wabe dou wi nure cwo, la to co kwen tiyagum cunaggin cuken.
\v 33 Di la kange bwe Basamariya nure tou co wi.
\v 34 Con bou fiyentange niwo wiye, bwacinen deti ya ci nuwa cinen neu, belti cinen nuwanko kange mwem bitutti (Inabi) kunn ken co yoken dor kelba cer yaki co fiye dami, na to co.
\v 35 Ki elfini con boki dinari yob ne ni luwe, yi co ki to twa cinen dero, tano mo twalki cum dige ma ne neri, na yilauri man ya nen.
\v 36 Mor nubo wuro we nii mo to ci nii bilang kange ce?
\v 37 Ni merangka ki nii wo nuncinen bilangtum, Yecu yii o ki ya manyo ken.
\v 38 Di ci yaekn ti Yecu doken mor conunkur kange nawiye kange dencerro Marta yo co lo co.
\v 39 Con wiki korya ce den do Maryamu, wo yi na Teluwe nuwa ti ka dike co toktiyeu.
\v 40 Marta ki ma yiri, la con bo Yecu nen ki Teluwe kwm nen bo, korya mi dob ye ma, m nage do tiki kwami? yi co ca tikang ye, Yecu ciya, la yi co Mart, mo kwon dor mwero dor diker dutce.
\v 41 La Nii durko ciya co ki “Marta mon yumom diker kila.
\v 42 Di la diker win tam yo maryamu tom ce diker yor yore, wo, nii mani a yo cimenti.
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 Bi dikange Yeecu kwob diloti fiye kange, kambo co dimeri, win mor nob bwanka ceko, Teluwe merang nyinen kwob ka dilo ko, na wo yuwana merang nob bwnag ka cebo nineu.
\v 2 Con yi ci ki no ka kwob dilo tiri kom tok ki. Te den mwero na tii wucak, Liyar mwero bo.
\v 3 Ne nyo dike nya ca tiyeu na kakuko ce.
\v 4 Cutang nyinen bwirang keret nyero, na wo nyo cutang nobo wo ma nyinen bwirang keretiye, yare ki nyo fiye duwaka.
\v 5 Yecu yi ci ki we more kume ki bi farak, an ya fiye cowiye ki dila la yi co ki farmi niye cen cun cari ta'ar.
\v 6 Wori kange farmi bo yam can nawo, ma manki dike ma ne coti na ca.
\v 7 La niwo more ciya ki kom yere, kweri man nungum nyilo miko, take mo kange bibeiyo lomi nyon daken. mani ma dol kwenka ti nan nenen carito.
\v 8 Mi yi kom, bwen co kwen co ne bo cari di, bifarako tiber ciyere mo nua kwenduwe, mo cinti mo kenan coti, an kweni nenen dike mo cuitiye?
\v 9 Mi ma yi komti, kom keni atam ne kom, kom do kan fiya, kom kwabi an wumkumen.
\v 10 Wuro kentiye ti yoi wuro dotiye ati fiya, take wuro kwa tiye an womcinen.
\v 11 We Te wuro bibwece kin jinge a ne co nacuwetiye nyi jinge?
\v 12 Kangeri ken co far di a neco bininge.
\v 13 na wo nyori kom nobo bwit kom nyom kom ne bibeiyo lo kume dike yori nye ye bwi Te kume wo mor dii kwama, an ne kom yuwa tangbe kwamako, nubo ken ce.
\v 14 kange diye Yeecu cok kange bwekelkele nyo tamtabe, la bwekelkele cirum niwo la a tok erti. Dike nyimankar tam nubo.
\v 15 Kange bo mor nobe ciki, “Kibi kwang Ba'alzabuba liya kelkeli cok kelkeli bo tiye.
\v 16 Kange bo cuwa co, cin do na cin nung cinen yirom dii kwama.
\v 17 Yeecu kweri nyomom dike ci kwati ner cire, la yi ci ki “Liyar do ti kangum yoberi, ki ma kiye ki bwiti ci, kayan. Tano luwe tikangum yobri, ki ma kiye an yarum.
\v 18 Tano bwekelkele tikangum yobri, kiye kange dorce, la liyar cero a ti nyi? kom ki maki cok. bwekelele ki bi kwan Ba'alzabuba.
\v 19 Tano man cok bwekelkele fiye ba'alzabuba, la kibi we burombo bwan kumen ti cok kelkelito tiye? nyori ci, ciyilam nobo a makumen bolang.
\v 20 Tano fiye kwama ni ma cok kelkelelito tiyeri, Liyar kwamaro biyeken kumen.
\v 21 Tano nii bikwangne ki kulen kiyener, ki cum lo cue kulen cere bi bu.
\v 22 Tano kange nii lamco ki bi kwan kuwam cori, an yom kulen kwener cero.
\v 23 wuro mani wari kange mo, kiye mati kange mo, take woro mani murti kange mo, watanka co matiye.
\v 24 Tano yuwatangbe ko bwir ko ceri bwi nii, ki do fiye kucer, ki do fiye ca fubom tiye. No fiya bori a yi ki, man yilaken lomi fiye ma do boweu.
\v 25 Na yilauri co fiya cin nyenum luwe, cin ywelum co.
\v 26 Ya an tou kange kelkeli niber wuro la co bwiranke ci bo ci yiken wi, cile nii wo an la kabako bwiraka.
\v 27 Kambo Yeecu tok tiyeri, kange nawiye mor nobe, kung dir cero ki, “Nii bibwiyere fwero bo neneu kange yori mo nowe.
\v 28 Nob bibwiyere wori nuwa ker kwamaro tiye ci bwnagtenti take.
\v 29 Fiya nobo yo ten mwerkako ti la co ki, kallo wo duwo, kallo bwir, do yiromti, bwen duwal yirom mani a nung cinentiye, kan yirom Yunusa.
\v 30 Na wo Yunusa yilam yirom nubo nineba, nyo bi bwe nifire a yila yirom ti fiye kalllo wo wiye.
\v 31 Nawiye wo ca liyar kudu an ti na ma bolang kange kaldo wo an twalum ci, ceru fiye kutan na co nuwa yilen suleimanu, la kange wo wuro la suleimanu fo.
\v 32 Nubo ninea an ti bolang kange nubo kaldo wo an kuwan ci. Cin nuwa fulenke Yunusa, cin yiloten, kange La Yunusa wo.
\v 33 Nii kan mani a kwer talkeri ti na yurangume, kaka Cimon ki tale, dil au yo denkila, be na ne filang mor kuwe.
\v 34 Nuwe mwe co talkire bwi mweutana nuwe mwe yora ri, tang num bwiyombo a fiya filang tano nue mani to ti yorari bwi kume a dim ka kumtacile.
\v 35 Kom ma yora kati filang ko kume nen yilam kumta cili. Tano bwi kume dimka filang di, kumtacile man.
\v 36 Tano bwi kume gwam dimka, kumtacile man biduwarece, la bwi kume a yilam na talkire wo ne filang cekoti durkumere.
\v 37 kambo Yecu dim kereri, kange nii dingle (Bafarice) cwo co na bo lo cona co cam cari, Yeecu dou yi.
\v 38 Kambo nii dingli (Bafarice) To Yeecu ca carito ti nirbo kang, la ti nyimange.
\v 39 Yeecu yi co ki, “Kom nod dinglibo” (Farisawa) kom ki nirum ka bwim kwelem more dimka duti kange chil.
\v 40 Kom kule nobe, wo ma bwimbe kebo wo ma moreka?
\v 41 Kom ne nob bwinebo dike more. Dikero gwam na nir kimen.
\v 42 Kwan kom nob dinglib Farisawa kom yo wine ti dor kwobe na kule, tibi kange tangnim laluwo, dila kom citan wucake kange cwika kwama ko. tam nyo na ma dike dong dong a cwi tangnin dikero tak.
\v 43 Gwam kume kom nob dinglib Farisawa kom cwiti a nekom fiye ken mor kurwabe, take a ne kom dur yarume fiye fene.
\v 44 Gwam kom nob dinglib Farisawa Kom ki no na tuwetinin bo ci yo cinen bo kange diker na yirome nobo ti fuwarangi kebo ki nyomka cek.
\v 45 Kange nii meranka mor bulange Yahudawa ciya karcinen ki Nii meranka dike mo toke, kangum ner nyera.
\v 46 Kwan kom nob meranka bulangeb dike kom kung nobo nin kulen do tuu lambi kwan tuka ke. Kom mok bo kulendo kibi wer kange kume.
\v 47 Kwankom, kom mu diker kulomkati fiye tuwetinin nob tomange kwama bonin.
\v 48 Bwikoko ten kwanib kumeb twallan ciye.
\v 49 Yilam ka nyom nangen tenkwanub kumebo, ci twalan nob tomangebo wo kom bulanti ki ciye,
\v 50 Kaldo a tuu tutum bwiyale nob tomangebo gwam wo ci twal fiya kale wo fwele.
\v 51 Tabti bwile habila ya tam ciko Zakariya ciko wo ci twal tiber tanjilan kwamero fiye wuccak. ong mi yi kom an do dike tam na ciye kaldo wo wiye.
\v 52 Gwam kom nob merangka bolangeb wo Yauhdawa ceu, wori kom tom nyilo yomka, kom ki bwikimi kom do bo. kom Yuwan do ka ko doka.
\v 53 Bwikako Yeecu dob fiye co nob mulankab kange nob dinglib (Farisawa) cin tu kurom kange co cin kwokangi kange co dor diker dutce.
\v 54 Ci doti na cin cii cimen kore, na ci tam cco mor dike co toktiye.
\c 12
\p 
\v 1 Kutang bo nyori bwikako nubo dutce mwerkang fwarang bwititi, La con ter tokak kererko kange bibei tomange ceu. Kom cire kange canfuwambo nob diglibo (Farisawa) wo co yulkako.
\v 2 Diker mani nawo cummome nawo mani a wom tiye, kange mani nawo yurangume, mani a nyomtiye.
\v 3 Diker mani wo ka tokti balumbale, wo mani a nuwati nyanglange, Dike kom toki kiyelange, an kwaki dir fiye gwam.
\v 4 Farub mib ma yi komti O-n nure tai wuro a twalum bwiyotiye. bwikako nye ci manki diker makar.
\v 5 Mi makumen biweret, wo ka nuwa tai cero tiye, kom nowo tai wuro twalum di an mwerken kom mor kira. “O” man yi kom ti kom nuwa tai co.
\v 6 Ke ciki meye berin bilebe nung anini yob? gwam nyo kwama mani a tabti ki wi more ciye.
\v 7 Kange yirito dor kumere nyomom kilatum ciyembo. Kom nuwa re tai kom la bilibetin do yorka fiye co wiye.
\v 8 Mi yikom ti Nii wo tok fulen miro kabum nobomeri, Bibwe nifire an warkercer kabum nob tomangeb kwama.
\v 9 Tak Nii wo koye kabum nobomeri man ko co kabaum nob tomange kwama.
\v 10 Nii na tok ker kiyer dor bibwe nii fireri an cutan cinenwi. La niwo tok kwilangka dor yuwa tangbeko wucakeri, mani a cutang cinenti.
\v 11 Tano ci bo ki kom kabom bikur waber di, kange kabum nob bulange kange kabum liyabem kom bwende kange dike ka kartiye nawo ka cerum dor kumerotiye; kange diker ka tok tiye.
\v 12 Yuwa tangbe ko wucake an meran kumen dike ka tok ti fiya co.
\v 13 Kange mor mwerkanka nin yi co ki Nii merangka yi kemi na tikangum kwalito kange mo.
\v 14 We yo yi nii bolange, kange nii do kertiye dor kumer?
\v 15 Kom yilam ki cini kari kom yilam nob kucunu kebo dike nii mweri co la dike yurak mor dumece.
\v 16 La Yeecu yici kero ki danke ki take ni kange ni carito dutce,
\v 17 Nii wo kwabi neer cer ki, ye ma matiye, wo ma mani ki fiye ma yom carito wo tiye.
\v 18 Ma nyo mom di ma matiye man werum binitin miro na mwirangum na yoken cari mito kang tannung dikro.
\v 19 La na yi dumek mi mike dume mi, mo wi ki diker dutce wo ci yomneneu fubom ca no ma bilantum.
\v 20 Di kwama yico nii wo mor kume wo ci ci dume mwetimunen. kulen do mo mweri mo yo dor mwero nineu a yi la na wee?
\v 21 Nyo niwo mwer dor ceronin cwika, tano co man ki cweka kwamamnin
\v 22 Yecu yibibei tomangece, Di nyo ma yi ti ki kome, kom bwende ki dume dike ka ca ti kaka wo ka dukti bwiyeu.
\v 23 dume la cari, bwiyo la kwilen.
\v 24 Kom to karce nii mani fi fik mani biye bituwe. Ci manki bentini kaka kuni murka carik, dila kwama catikici, kom kon la bilibe yorka?
\v 25-26 We more kume, ka tii dilanka a yok dor cero nin ten kumeni tiye? tana kom dolbo ko yok dorkumero ninten dikero bi duware. Ye bwi ka kwom dor kumero ti kange tangnim dikereu?
\v 27 Kom to funti mor kiye kambo ci duyantie. ma ci ma nange, ma ci ma kange diker. Mi yi komti bwen Culeimanu ki bwayilen cero dwal di, du bo kulen do la ciye yerake.
\v 28 Tano kwama dii yerako nin kulen yori na nyori, den i, fini an dokken co kira, la a bwi nyi kwama a fweti mani ca dukumen kulentiye, kom nubo ki dwal ka bilenkere.
\v 29 Kom bwende ki dike wo ka catiye kaka wo ka notiye, kom kimang deu.
\v 30 Nyo nubo dor bitinen gwam ci do dike wuroti, take Te kume nyomom kom ti cwi dike buromboti.
\v 31 Kom do liyar cero, kullendo wuro ciya yok kumenti.
\v 32 Kom nuware tai, kom bi beiyo bi duwattinim wori ki bilang tum Te kume a ne kom liyartiye.
\v 33 Kom miyem dike kom cike kom ne nob fuwabbo. kom ma dor kumero nin bilantin we mani a kayatiye kom yoken di kwama fiye dike cuwo mani a difiye, fiye nob kub mani a dol yaka tiye, nakunkunge mani a kanti.
\v 34 Fiye cweka mwe wiye firn nermwero wiye.
\v 35 Kom mwatumen cwentum kulen kumero ko cakkangum, talkire kume ata cai kang kang.
\v 36 Kom yilam na nuboro wuro nintan teluwe ciye na yilau lo cika, la tano bo kwa yilokori can can do wo ciya kweni ci wobcicnen yiloko.
\v 37 Bilenker ma yikom ti an cakkangum kulencer na yo ci yiranken la na ceci carito. ki bwici.
\v 38 Bwen Teluwe ciya a bo ki kume keno, kaka ki dii ca biyerci ki bati ci ningtan co ti. Nobbibwer cnga buro.
\v 39 Ko nyomom na nii luwe nyomom boka nii kwiye kori, mana a dobti ci wercinen luwe, ci doken.
\v 40 Kom ti ki bati wari kom nyomom filang Bibwe nii a yilautiye.
\v 41 Bitru yi co ki teluwe nyo mwo yin danke wotiye, kaka nubo gwam ka?
\v 42 Teluwe to ki nii durko wuni ki cini nii yilen wo Teluwe ce ne co canga ceti kangeceke, na to ci na ne ci carito fiya daten ne?
\v 43 Nii bibwiyer canga wuro Teluwece a fiiya co na dike ci yoce ca mane.
\v 44 Bilenke mi yikom ti aneken co lo ceu kang cek.
\v 45 Ta no canga wo toki mor nerci ki Teluwe m lakken boka ko, la con ter bukka tang nim cangambo nabarub kange natub, farub nagenebce.
\v 46 Teluwe canga wo an yilau, fiya co nyombo, La torangum co ki mwan ki mwan na mwe co kange nubo manki ciniye.
\v 47 Canga wo nyomom mulen Teluwece, di la ka bo bati mabo dike teluwece yoco ca mane diker wo Teluwe cwitiye, a nuwa bibuker kange banjange dutce.
\v 48 La niwo nyombe, la ma dike kebo dong dong, mani a nuwa bi buker kange banjange dutce. Nii wo ci neco dikero ducce a do dikero ducce cinen. Tano ni wo ci neco diker ducce na takako ce, na a do dike ducce kambo ken cinen.
\v 49 Ma bou be na dukti kira dor bitiner, man cwi na ki kweri tam di.
\v 50 Mo man wi ki yuka mwenge ko wucake wo ciye mamentiye ciko, la ma cwi mwini mam.
\v 51 kom kwa netti, ma bo dor bitiner na boki for neret? ma yi kome o-ong dila yalkanka.
\v 52 Tabti nawo an fiya nubo nung mor luwe wiin di ciya tikangum, nubo ta'ar makiye ti kange nubo yob, yob makiye ti kange ta'ar,
\v 53 Bwe kange te ciyan ma kiye kange bwiti ci, bwe an makiye kange Tece, Ne an makiye kange bibwece bobya, bobya kange nece, bifire kange ferce, wi bibwe ce kange ferce.
\v 54 Yecu yi nubo mwerummeu, no kom to yuwa mwengek kwenu meri komki mwembo an cwe, nyo a matiye.
\v 55 Tano yuwa ko ceru bangdi komki an ma cillen kambo ken, nyo matiye.
\v 56 Nubo bwir, kom yumon fwetanka kabal kalero kange dii kwama, dila lakom nyom bo fwetanka dikeko bwiti nawo nyeu?
\v 57 Ye bwi kom nyombo dike a tikankomtiiye?
\v 58 Tano mwi yaken ti kubolange kange kobkanka mweri, ken co kom ywellum don nuret kari ya kinen kabum nii bolange. Kari nii bolange neken nen nii wo to fucina tiye mani a nung mwen nyomkankati fucina.
\v 59 Mi yimnen mani mo ceru ti, mon yam kiyemero ci bwangmwen tiyeu.
\c 13
\p 
\v 1 Ki kwama curo nubo kangem wi yico ker dor nobo Galiliye wo Bilatu ceikangum bwiyale ceu kange wabi.
\v 2 La kiritti yici, “kom kwatiri Galatiyawambo bwiran kere ka?
\v 3 Nyonin, min yi komti. No kom dobbori gwam kume kom bwiyarangi na ci.
\v 4 Kakaa nobo kwobcilombo naurube ciloam wo luwe cwemi nyeu yar cinenti dorceer ci bwiyarangume, kom kwatiri ciin la tangnum nobeu urucalimau biranke?
\v 5 O-ong, miki. Lano gwam niwo ko dobka ri ciyan bwiya rangum.
\v 6 Kiritti tok dangke wuro,”Nii kange wi ki tii nyongjong wo ci fiken mor take ce la cin bou na ci ca bituttuiyeri la tiyo man ki cari.
\v 7 Dila nii curo yi nii tokako,'to, coro ta'ar naweu, ma do bituttuiti fo nyongjongo nin di mafiyabo tom co ye bwi ba dob coti ten fiye ti koniye?'
\v 8 Co nii tokakko ciya toki neye kumeni nyo bi dob na kam nan yoti cinenti kilongwi
\v 9 No mabi tuttidi cortini boti yeri tano mabobi tuttiri nan mwatum co.
\v 10 Bi di kange Kiriti ma mrngkati fiye bi wabe kange bidiye fob ka.
\v 11 Di la naweu kangee bou wo dii curo kwob cilombo narub wiki twirak yuwa bwir gwam kange fwinka mani do taka ti.
\v 12 Kambo Kiriti to ce cin cuwaco yico cin cukum twirako wo.
\v 13 La kiriti yoti kanko dor ce tabbo. buri can cando cin tarken cet co ter bilonge liyar kwamma.
\v 14 Di ni kur biwaro manfunerr dige bwiyeu Kiriti nangen bi Fob ka di ni bi wabiro nyi nubo kume ni wi nyo nukku na nangen do ce kom bow na makimen ddi La kebbo ki bidiko fobka.
\v 15 Di la teluwe kar cimen ki kom nubo bwir no nyori mi wor tiber kimer mi kange wo ca ki gelbati na fiye ci tekume nemwem bidiye fobka ka?
\v 16 No nyori wuro bibwe Abrame wo be kelkele no bwamco ki coro kwab culom nanrube, tano nyo mania kwi cati kibi diye fubka ka?
\v 17 Kambo co tokki nyo weri nubo ma kwab kangka ti kange coweu cin nuwa kwenduwe. Gwam tare al cin ma fur nener ki dikero kendo wuro ci mane.
\v 18 Kiriti toki kiye ba tak liyar kwama ti cike yilo ye ba dang ti cike?
\v 19 Wi nyo na nun nying cin wuro ni kange wabi takece Landim nyo gili gili la bilibe tini manag cor tini kani ce nen.
\v 20 Yila con tokko liyar kwararo ba tok kiye?
\v 21 Wi nyo ca fuwam di la kange nawiye mwe kange mim murduwe bidigle tar na fumco.
\v 22 Kiriti ker kan cinar lor kange bwar lor, wi nuro wo yakenti Ucalima ci mernag cinneti.
\v 23 La cin yi co teluwa nubo biro ciya fiya dob kakko bi dob nyo ka? La cin yici.
\v 24 Ki ma dige dateneu. ki do nure bwa ki do nure bwabwa leli nyori mi nyi kom, nudo ducce ci cwi doka ti di la ci fiyabo doka.
\v 25 No niluwe kwri kwenum nungum yilokko la kan tiken kale kom kwa kwabang nyi lokkoti teluwa, teluwe do nyo nyi do mour di cin ciya cotaki mi nyomkombo keno kom cirou feri.
\v 26 Di la ka tok komki nyim ca nyin no for kabum mwem. di la mun merang nyinen dor nure nyim bo nin.
\v 27 La can ciya ci tokki.
\v 28 Ciyan ci wiye kange kuka nunne ki bidiye kom to muca, kange Isaku kange Yakubu gwam nob dugume firer liyar kwama kumeu ciyan merken kom kale.
\v 29 Ci ya bo twat mee, bang, kole ci ya ca tokam cari iyar kwama.
\v 30 Ki nyim comm wuro nob kaba nyim lam nubo cuwa bwire nubo cuwa bwireu co nubo yilam kaba.
\v 31 Di kutabo kangem faricawa cin bou ciki Musa, kubom fo dike bwiyeu Hiridus cwi twalka mwekti.
\v 32 Kirititi tokki com ya Bicura kom ki to min co kom ninga nubo fiya fulo ki di ki kume take cwiti a murangu bibeiyo na wuro bicate ki murang de bi bei loce mwor tangum cem la kom ciyabo.
\v 33 To ci miran lomwe la mi, yikomti mani ka to yeti tano diye ki tokke luma drek tam nyo ki den kwamar.
\v 34 Bwentano a manyiri yam mimbo ya kenti duwen, fini cike daten bo ciya twalum teluwe kutom kange Ursalima.
\v 35 Kom to lo kumeu cin cwutanwi No kom tok kumki luma ki no kan bibwe nii wo bilang kwama yeu.
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 Di fubka cin do ko lo ni wo mor farisawa na cin ca cari la nubo cor ci nenten nuwe.
\v 2 Di la ikange wo ka co wo ki der na cekke.
\v 3 Kiriti me nobbi finero durko kange fari cawa daten na fulani bidiye fobka nyo kakka mani nyo ka?
\v 4 La cin kumom Kiriti ta co fulo co di nyico ca yakenti
\v 5 La kiriti me ci wetiber kimer ki bwe kange, bi curan di yraken bwire bidiye fubka la mani ca cokk ti ka?
\v 6 Di la dol bo tokker diger buronin.
\v 7 kambo Kritti to nubo ci cuowu d ti ka fiye yime keneu tok kerg dangke ci nen.
\v 8 no ni kange cowonner fiye nakarim yire dur ni kange wi ci cuwoco kenne lanen ki dur.
\v 9 Di la no niwo cuwo kom bou an yinen nub niwo mi fiye yimemweu na coyeu mwan kweni mu yiken kutule bi duware.
\v 10 No cin co nen fiyeri, yiken kutule biduware la no niwo co nenu bouri atin tooki farmi kweni yiken fo cwemer na fiya bi duyet nuwe nubo wuro nokom yi wariye.
\v 11 Gwam nitu dor core ci kebo diker ciyan bilange co tano niwo dor cero cin diker nubo mani a bilank coti.
\v 12 Kritti yila yi nii wo co cue no mo neni cari na ti na cwentiri yire muki mwan cowo for nener yimom ki namwe, niwo bidom kange mwe di dike ci ca mani nyo.
\v 13 No mwon cuwofiye nakari cuwang kang niwo mani cike fukma, kilen wale kange bibei.
\v 14 Mwan fiya luma dike bwiyeu ci ma bilantum dikero wo mwa ma cineneu ma ci ya neneti na bilank Yeecu maneu mwan fiya bilanka kibi diye kwenka nob bi bwiyer kwama.
\v 15 Kambo ni win mor nubo ca carito kom wari kange kiritti nuwa nyori ki lima nubo biro a ca cari liyar kwama.
\v 16 La Kiriti yi co ki ni kange wi cowo nubo ducce ki cika dur
\v 17 Kambo di cika ko lameri tom cange ceu yaca cowo nubo wuro co ne tomanage ciya bour dikero kwarub ywelu.
\v 18 Gwam ciye cinter neka dige bwiyeu. wo kiba yico min tiyen takke daten yamman to mi kinong nenti dobye.
\v 19 La ni kange tokki min tiyen nne nung mi cwiti nan cuwa mi konog nenti dobye.
\v 20 Ni kange ki nia na nawiyeu mani ma dol yakati.
\v 21 Kambo bwe canga ce bo yi teluwe ceri yaken tiyeri la teluwe ceu mam funer nyi canga ceu ki ya wulom bwangten nure cinar loreu kange wo kebo cinar loreu. congawu, fukma, kilen celeb, waleb.
\v 22 La canga ceu tokki i lomi dike mo tikke timi mam dila corbo bwini.
\v 23 Di la ni luweu nyi canga ceu ya bangten nureu cinar loreu kange wo bwar lor bolange ciya dou na ci dim lomi.
\v 24 Tano nyi mi yi komti win more kume cowo ki kaba bakeu, kange ciye mani a c ci kamiti.
\v 25 Nyo tere yakenti kange co la con yila bwi yi ci.
\v 26 Gwam niwo bou fo fiye weu tano kobo tece, nece, wice, bibiyoloce, yitum cebo nina bare kange wice nyo kange nercero ri, mmani ca yila bibwemiti.
\v 27 Gwam niwo tuba bwatiye na bwangmenten neri kebo bibwemi.
\v 28 We tiber kumer wo cwi muka luweti la yibo na nyi mom diek ca kwale ki kaba tano cin wi ki kiyemer tak kakkori?
\v 29 Tano nya ci yo kwar kuwero ci takbo dikakori nubo biro toeu nung coti.
\v 30 Ci tokti kii niwo ter muka la fwem ki di kakko.
\v 31 No nyori liay wini wo yakenti kange liya kange nyombo bi kwama nubo loce keno nyiri daten bikwan tin mamdi na ci nyi mom keno niwo ki nubo bikeate kwab ki culomeu catin mam kange niwo bikate kwini yoberi.
\v 32 Tano mani ca doltiri ki kwama kece firen kutaneu ca tom canga na meu yaka nanneko na ka kwendo mani.
\v 33 Nyori ni kange mani tiber kumer wo ca dubom kulen cero tiri mani ca yila bibwe miti.
\v 34 Mam dike yora tano carum bitineri mwa ma ye?
\v 35 Man ki luma bi tine tano amnyiri dam cutangka gwam niwo kitu nuwa kange ca nuwa
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 La yuwak nob merangkab kange nob yoka kemer doreko bouti Yeecu nen cin nuwacoti.
\v 2 Farisawa kange nob mulangka bo cima fwenati bwitici ciki” Niwo yo nob bwirangkebti ci ca caitoti waritak.
\v 3 Yeecu tok danke wo yici.
\v 4 Canno kange kume ki kwame kumi kwo lawin more ce lem, mani ca dob kwini Teer culombo teere ti naci bwanten meka wuro win lemeu naci fiyam.
\v 5 Tano ci fiyam ri naci tuu ci yaken Lagwamcem ci no fuwor nerer tiye.
\v 6 No ci yilaudi naci cwo farubcebo kange nubo biom kange ceu, naci yici, kom ti kanye fuwor nerer min fiya kwame mi lemeu.
\v 7 Miyikomti nyo a ma fuwor nerer tiye dii kwama don ni bwiranker win kange nobo kiner luma kwini taar culombo teereu wuro dobo ywelka bwirange keu cereu.
\v 8 Kaka we nawiye, ki kemer nai nyo kwob no lemdi manica wentalkire ti ci nyina yum mor kuwe la citi doi naci fiyam me?
\v 9 Noci fiyam laci mwer farubcebo kange nubo bidom kange ceu ciyicii kom tikanye fuwor nerer min fiyam kwame meu.
\v 10 Nyo mi yi komtiye, diker fuwer nerer nob tomangeb kwamab cano, ni bwinrangke winn dob bwirangkerori.
\v 11 La Yeecu yici “Ni kange wi ki bibei bayilob yob.
\v 12 La bi duwareu yi teece Tee neye miu kwalito mor cuweka mwekonin. Dila Tee ce kabkamm cinen kwalito.
\v 13 Ki Kumeni kilabori dila bwe biduware murance kwalito yaken biti kange katangi. cin yakcangum kwalito tie nen bikulentiti yakcangum kemero cero noranka diker.
\v 14 Kambo ci yakcangum kwalitori la cin ma wura kambo ken bitine con ni lam doken bwini.
\v 15 Yacin neken dorcero nangen ni kange bitineco, la twamom mor tangini ce nacinen Bilerce cariti.
\v 16 La cin cari ca do dike bilerece a catiyeu, wori ni kange mani neco cariti.
\v 17 Dila kambo yulancero bwiceri yice ki cnga Tee mi cingile cike cari la cinnen bo dila mi fo ma bwiyati ka ker carity.
\v 18 Man kweni neken Tee mi in yico “Tee Min ma dikwanin bwirainke min kangmwen.
\v 19 Ma datenbo coya muki bibwemiri yokenye min yilam win mor cangabtinim mweb?”.
\v 20 Lacin kweni, cibou tecemin. Dila kambo ci kutanneri, la Tee ce tomco cibwini ceto yaki cwak, yan bwabco, lata macinen cuika.
\v 21 Bweu inyico Tee, mi ma dii kwama nen bwiranke, min kangum mwen. ma labo coten ye muki bi bwemwe.
\v 22 Di la Teece yi cangab cebo, kom bouki bellewo yor yoreu, kom ducinen kon dok cinen keneu kange cek kange ta nacek.
\v 23 la ko bou ki neneu mobiyeu kom biyem bima cenen bilengtum ciko.
\v 24 Na weu bebwemi bwiyam fiyeco dila naweu yilau ki dume. Lem fiyeco dila fiyau. lacin teer cika.
\v 25 Ki kwama co bibwece durko ki kambo dadom loweri cin nuwa ci kwaban dikerti kange nuwetinin.
\v 26 Lacin com kange bwe canage loceu meco dikerowo mati loriyeu. neneu mob mobeu wori cin yilau lo kwamer.
\v 27 Bwe cangau yico kemwe yilau lowe, Tee mwe biyem neneu cin yilau lo kwamer.
\v 28 Di la kece bwe durko mam funer ko do kako mor luwe Tee ce ceriu kale kinang co.
\v 29 Bwe durko ciyace Tee ce ki to ka cotiyowo mi ari kange mo ki komwem bo tomange nii wucak kange wo mune yob be nibeni wo ma cati kange farub mibeu.
\v 30 Di la bwe wuro ya cutang bicir mwer dor mun biye cinen kalnenero mob mo bo.
\v 31 Di la Teece yico ki “Bibwemi, mu wari kange mo gwam dikero na mi yeri na mwe.
\v 32 Di la dong dong cimamwen luma kange fur nerer, wori kemwe wo buyam dila nawori ki dume, fiayco lem la nanweu, bin fiyam.
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 Yeecu yi nobbwankecebo tak, “nii cuwekako kangeni ki ni toman'nye, Lacin kwa kiyan nye ki nii toman nyewo kang cineut cuwekacokob.
\v 2 La nii cuweka wuco yico, “fulan yer minuwa dor mwere? bowki kiyeka tomange mweke, wori mari mwa yila nii tomange mititak.
\v 3 Lamitomange toki neren, ma mangi, nilomi anyam tomanyewo kangmik? Wo, mimanki bikwantonet lami cwa kwenduwe meka cekoti.
\v 4 Minnyumwom dike ma matiyeu noci cukumye mor tomanye nindi, nubo ayoye lonici.
\v 5 Dila nitomannye cwuningangum nubo teluwece bwanteng centiyeu, yi nii kaba, Nyi nii lomi bwangmwenten tiye?
\v 6 yiki, 'nuwannye kwini kwob' Isryico, Bifumer mwerowo, canakowo yikenyiye, mulangum kwini nung.
\v 7 Yilan yikannye, ciki bwangmwentuniyi? Yiki, cwayi bikate kwini kwob, 'bifumerwo mulangum kwini narub'.
\v 8 Dila niwo caklang nii bwini bilengewo ki yulancero. Bibeyo kaleweu nyimem maka nyinong nubo ko kaleweu la bibei filange yulang.
\v 9 Miyi komti komma bifarak kannge cuweraka kannge buni bilinke, cawo cin dimri, naci yokom lonici wuro manki diks.
\v 10 Wo madikerti dongdong dor dikero biduwareri, cin nii dongdonge dor dikero dur, wo kebo nii bilinke don dikero bidurure, kebo ni bilinke dor dikero dur.
\v 11 Tano kommabo dike dongdonge di cuwekako kebo wucakeri, we aciya kumenti kicuweka wabilinkece?
\v 12 No komma dike dongdonge ki kemer niidir we anekom kemer kumer tiye?
\v 13 Kange mami wo a wob nii luweti yobe, catin kowini, ci cui win kakka ci ciya winening, ci cuwe kangum wineu. mani ka wab kwaamatiri kom wab cuwekati.
\v 14 Kambo faricawabo wuro cui cuwekatiyeu nuwa dikero biombori, cin macinen cuwelangka.
\v 15 Inyici, “Kom ko tiki dor kumero kabum nubem, dila kwaama nyumuom nerkumero. Dikero nubo nedurketiye nyeu diker yeika fiye kwaama wiye.
\v 16 Biwerer bifumer nob tomangebo inwi yakenciko Yahaya nin. Kwama wuro cin bwanten ker liyar kwaaranarotiye, kwarub kutannyi kwamacuo ci bwangten ker liyar kwaamarotiye, kwanrub ci ma bwi dokka dorekti morece.
\v 17 Gwamm kangero, atin yilam bwaibo diko kange bitineu nabecum, na diker win nabi weretro na dim.
\v 18 Niwo nyankan wucenin naukangeri inma buroka, ken niwo nau nawiyewo cinyam kanngeri inma buroka.
\v 19 Nii cuwakakko kanngenwi, wo dukulen kemero yoryoreu nuwa luma kalecokoti.
\v 20 Cin yoken nii kini kannge nyiloco, dencero Liazaru, wo bwiceu ka deti.
\v 21 Ceu ci cuiti naci bwam fwercero ki fiti cari yarangum ti fiye caka carik nii cuweka nyo kibi cuwetincer bom biyablam bwiceti.
\v 22 Laniwo bwiyamri, nobtomangeb kwaamabo tu co yakenciko Ibrayim nin. Ni cuweks buyam, cin fwerumco,
\v 23 ci mor Adece ci nuwa dotange ti, la cin kun doro cinto Ibrayim kutan, kan'nge Liazaru cantangcek.
\v 24 Lacin cobicoro ciki, Tee Ibrayim, ci bwinni mito, twomun Liazaru adokti biwurece mwem abelti menti biyenmin, wori indotange minuwati mor kirewe.
\v 25 Dila Ibrayim yico, Bwe, kwabi ki kwamawo mu kalemweu munuwa luma cuweka mwekobi, munyo kulentinimbo ken, La Liazaru nuwati ka dotange. Dila naweu luma cinecotide, mwe munuwa dotangeti.
\v 26 Nobo nyori dila buwako cuwa cuwau inwi, wori birombi coi yabkati kumeneu nadolde, tak kannge na yabuurefo nyinnen.
\v 27 Lamicuweks yiki, Lami kennenti Tee Ibrayim, twornco lo Tee ni-
\v 28 wori minweki keb mib bi beibayilobe nyo nung, amincinen biweret kayilo cibuo fiye dotangewo.
\v 29 Dila Ibrayim yiki, cin wiki Musa kannge kannge nob toman'ngebi nyori ciya nuwaci,
\v 30 Dilla nii cuweka ciyaki, 'O, on, Tee Ibrayim, cano kan'nge mor birombo biyam biya yacinendi, ciyam yiloten.
\v 31 Dilla Ibrayim yico, cono ci Musa kan'ge nobtoman'gebo ri, cabunano kan'nge fulou duwendi maciya nuwacoti”
\c 17
\p 
\v 1 La Yeecu yi nob bwankacebe, “nyimaka mami ter kottangka wo adokbo maka bwirank kektiye dila cilkakiniwo a yilam cotiyeu!
\v 2 Can nyimiri kin yei cimenti ner kuwaka kwircer amerkanco mor fara kan'nge wo ca yilam diker kottanka biduwatinimbo wuronin.
\v 3 Kom yabki dor kumer. No kemwe kanngumdi, werangco, cano ciyilotendi dobcinen.
\v 4 Cano kanmwen kiriti niber kikakukowimdi yilam bou munen kiriti niber yiki, min yiloten, yilam nyo dobcinen”
\v 5 Dilla nobtoman'gebo cinyi Teeluwe, “cuob nyienten bilingkeu”.
\v 6 Teeluwe lanyiki, “Cano komki bilinke duwali na nun bikateri, mwanyi tiyowo, kwomfo, ya kulken mor caji”, atim manyo.
\v 7 Canwe more kume carno wiki cawonya wuro cuo cinen tomboti kakaa tocinen kwameti, cano yilam kiri, ayicoti, canokono bouyifo na camcarito?
\v 8 Mani co yicoti ki mamen diker nan cam, na bwam dak mwekori maman na'nyend benan dimcaka carito kan'nge noko mu'ngeko?
\v 9 Manica ma cariya cewonin buka kamin yekti wori madikeci dokco ciya mane, keno am mani nyori?
\v 10 Nyo, cano kom bwanten ciyikomemri, lakom toki, 'nyin can'nya manki nanyene. Nyim ma dikewo tam kang'eu”.
\v 11 Kakuko kamnye ciyakenti Wurcalimani lacim bwanteng beten Samariya kan'nge Galili.
\v 12 Kambo cidokenti cunnuku kan'nyeri, dila bayiloto kan'ngerobo kwob ki wale citim kutan cinkicico.
\v 13 Lacin kun diro “Yeecu, Tee kwama, cibwini nyeto”
\v 14 Kaci tociyeri, yici, “yakom dang dor kumero nob waberonin”. Yilam kambo ciyakentiyeri lacin yilam wucak.
\v 15 Wiri morece kacito cin cerco wucak keri, yilanken, duktang kwama kidiro kwamer.
\v 16 Cin yari kabum Yeecu, cin bucinen kamti. Cin ba Samariye.
\v 17 Yeecu in ciya toki, “kebo kwob ci ceri wucakka? infe tanneceu?
\v 18 Kan'nge mani wo yilam nekwaama durke kanco fabewo kikwaca?”
\v 19 Lanyico, “Kwoni yayam mwem. Bilinke mweu ceerner”.
\v 20 Kambo Faricawa meco kwamawo liyar kwamaro aboutiyeu, Yeecu ciya nyiki, “Liyar kwaamaro kobo nyomka maticike.
\v 21 Mani atokti, 'iriwo!' Kakaa, 'wurenhim!' Wori Liyar kwaamaro kino tiber kumer”
\v 22 Yeecu yi nob bwankabo, “Kumeni wi bouti nawo ka yoner toka kume win mor kumeni bi bwe niggire, dilla mani ka toti.
\v 23 Ciyan yikon, “Tofiren! 'Tofuo!' Dila kom yakomtore, kakaa kom bwangten cire.
\v 24 Nawo meblankako Nefilanti nafo cunya di kwamaka wori ya ken cunya di kwamako wureno, Nyo bi bwe nii a yilanyo ki kume bokaceko.
\v 25 Dila kang catin nuwe dotangetinim kidimen kidimen bwiriri, nubo kaleweu ankoco.
\v 26 Kambo bwi kal Nuhu re, nacuwo tak a bwiuti ki kwama bibwe nii aboutiyeu.
\v 27 Citi cai, citi noi, citi nai, cinakenti yaken di ye Nuhu doken Nabire kwama la mwom wermakabo bow twalan'gum ci kwarub gwamm.
\v 28 Nyo cimani ki kwama lutuwe, citi cai, citi noi, citinenii, citi miyei, ci fi fikkoti, cimuran'ngi.
\v 29 Dila kikakuko Lutu, cerum Saduma, lakira kwaamako caruu dikwama, twalan'ngum ci gwamm.
\v 30 Nyotak abwiuti ki kume bibweni aboutiye.
\v 31 Kikakuko wori, niiwo dor kureu ayiraure kica tu kulencer mor luwe. Nyotak niiwo kiyeu ayilaure.
\v 32 Komkwaki wii Lutu.
\v 33 Niwo cwidumecetiyeu, anlemco, lano niwo lem dumeceri, anfiyanco.
\v 34 Miyikomti, kumewo amfiya nubo yob kwangni win. Atim tumwin nadubomwimeu.
\v 35 Atim fiya natubo yob ci kuwa nerti ware. Atim tum win na dubom win.”
\v 36 
\v 37 Atim to nubom yob kii, “Antum win nadubom win”.
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 Yilam netenti dangke kwange ki yori kabo nyirinyir ciya kwo diloti ciya cwaretai,
\v 2 toki, “Bitine kam'nge nii bolan'nge kam'ngenwi baniki tai kwaama, takri manito yorinubek.
\v 3 Nawiye kwale kam'nge inwi bitineco, wobou cinenneu, yicoki, 'Tikanaye ka ma manob kiyeb mibonin luma tiyeu.
\v 4 Inkutan'nyi mani cwiti citikanyco, dila kibwiri toki mor nerece, cano mani cwatan kwaamati, takri mami mito yorak nubekti,
\v 5 kwarub kan'nge wo nwori nawriye kwalewo kwomye, mantikameo nacifiya luma, kambo marice luwayeti kiboko minenneu.”
\v 6 Dila Tee kwaama jiki, komuwa dikero nii bolangewo manki tokkeu.
\v 7 Lanawo kwama mani cor nubolocemboni birombo cicnen wiyeti kume kan'nge kakuke bwini citotika? Anmabwi fiye tikalicika?
\v 8 Miyikomti, comcorcinen bwimicito wulom. Dilla kambo bibweni bouweri, an kwobti bilam ke nii dor bitinen”
\v 9 Yilam neten Dankewo kange nubonin birombo ciya ki dorcireu, ki cimnob lumabeb, laci cuwekamten tankne nuboti,
\v 10 “Nubo kan'ngumbo cin doken mor lo kwama naci kwob dilo-win bwe Faricawa, wineu inni nye dotiye.
\v 11 Dila bwe Faricawa kweminti, kwodila dor dikero birombo dorcer, kwama, min buwen kang, mikebo natangne nob kwiyeb, nubo mamki cakcakeu, nubo ma burokatiyeu, kakaa namiwo yodotiye.
\v 12 Mimana kyak kiriti yob mor kume niber. Mine wineuti dorkwobberonin mordike mafiya.
\v 13 Dila niwa yodiker dorertiyeu tiken kutan, ciyabo nacikun dorcedil, dila kwa cangeang cekoti titokiki, kwaama, ci bruini bwinimito, minni bwiranke.
\v 14 Miyikombi, niwo yilaken loco fiyam cerke, kebo nawineu, cawo niwo kunderceri ciyatim yirau kico, lano niwo yiran kidor cero takeri ciyatin kumkenci.
\v 15 Dila nubo bocinenti kibi beyo naci teici, kambo nob bwankacebo to yeuri cin werankci.
\v 16 Dila yeecu cuoci fiye ciwiyeu, toki, “komdob bi beyo biduwartinimbo abou fiye niwiye, kom ywacire. Liyar kwaama na kalciroce.
\v 17 Bilinke miyikomti. canowo yobo liyar kwaamaro bwebi duwari, mani cadoti”.
\v 18 Kan'age dur nubere kan'nge mecoki nii meranka dike yoryore”, ye ma mati nsa fiya dume mankidike?
\v 19 Yeecu ciyaco, “Yebwi mucoye ni madike yoryoretiye? Nikange mani womadike yoryoretiyo nobons kwaama win cardi.
\v 20 Mwa nyimom werfudo-mare kayaka, twaldini, kure kwii, cwerde cwerke, ne Tee mwe kan'nge Nee mwe durko”.
\v 21 Di liyawo yiki, minmamwo kwarub kikwama min bwebwoyileu”.
\v 22 Kambo Yeecu nuwa nyeri, yico. Dikero win cwar kumwene. Miyem dike mucikeu kwarub, neken nubowe mancikeu, manfiya lo kwaama-ladina bou nwangmenten.”
\v 23 Kambo nicuwaka nuwa dikero biromberi, kan'ngum nercerobicom, wori cinni cuweka kamboken.
\v 24 Kambo Yeecu tonercoro kayommeri, lantoki, “An bwai nob cuwakab nidokin liyar kwaamar.
\v 25 Atim yilam bwarinin naa Telemeko nadoken buwak bilifarak, kan'nge ni cuweka doken liyar kwaamar.”
\v 26 Nubowa nuwa keroweu nyoki, “nokino nyori we abumtiye?”
\v 27 Yeecu ciya, nike lambi kwannifireu, deker makar fiye kwaama nuyeu.”
\v 28 La Bitru intokiki, “Nwo, nyin dubom dike nyicikeu kwarub nyin bwangtennen.”
\v 29 Yeecu nyici, Biki cwom nikan'nge nani dob locuti, kakaa wice, kaka kebcebo, kakaa Teebcebo kakaa bibiyoloceu, ker liyar kwaamar.
\v 30 Lamamica fiyati kiriti kiriti fo kalewenin, kan'nge dume diriye kalewo boutiyenin.
\v 31 Kamboci mwerci kwocilombo yoberi, nyici, “Inno, biyakenti wurcalima, kwarub dikoro ci mulan'ngi dor bi bwe niner kan'nge kang nobtoman'ngeb dukumebeb atim dim.
\v 32 Ciyar nekanco kan buboko yombo kwaamau, ci buwoco, cineco dofan'nge, citwomcinen bitom.
\v 33 Ciyam malico, citwalumco, ankwenum ki kume taareu”.
\v 34 Dilaciyom winwo mor dikerobirombonin, wori kerowo yuran'ngum yuran'nge fiyeciwiyeu, ci yomtenbo dikeci tokeu.
\v 35 Kambo cidadom Jeriko, ri fukwa kan'nge inwo yimcun'nya nurek, kenkiniti,
\v 36 kacinuwa kalinube cukentiyeri, lacinme nye bweitiye,
\v 37 Yeecu Banazret cuken tiye.
\v 38 Dila fukmau kundir kibikwan tokkero, “Yeecu, bibwe Dauda, Cibwini mito. Dala birombo kabeu werangco, ciyicoki kumwom.
\v 39 Dila kunten diro kibi kwan kamboken inyiki, “Bibwe Dauda cibwini mito.
\v 40 La Yeecu tim inyici ciyaboukico cinen. Kambo fukma bou bidomer, La Yeecu meco,
\v 41 ye mu cwitin mamwene? “inyiki, Tee kwaama, micwitin tofiye.”
\v 42 “Yeecu inyico, “yotoka fiyeko, bilinkemweu nirumnen.”
\v 43 Wi dangjang fiya toka, kwangteng Yeecu, duktang kwaamati. Cito nyori, lanubo kwarub caklang kwaama.
\c 19
\p 
\v 1 Yeecu do yarico la cukenti morece.
\v 2 Nikange wi deu cero zakka, dur nobo yo dortiye, nii cwika,
\v 3 Con mani no co to keno we yecudi. La co dol bo toka wor, nobo durce, take con nii bi kwen.
\v 4 Laco cukken kab ya con kwiken tii nyincin naco tom co, wori Yeecu acuwi fonure cuwonin.
\v 5 Kambo Yeecu lau weyeri kung nuwe dii layico ki zakka yi rau wulom daten mwo da lomo.
\v 6 La yilau wulumm-wulum yuwo co ki fuwor neret.
\v 7 La gwam ciye cin to wori, ci ma fwennati ki, ya fura lo nii bwiranke.
\v 8 Zakka kweni tii, ki to Teluwe, man. Kabkangum cweka miko more yob nane fuwa wine tana man yodiger nii cum wo ma yotiyeri, ma yila neti kiriti na'ar.
\v 9 Yeecu yi coki duwen fuloka bou fo luwe wurini nii co bi bwe Ibrayim.
\v 10 Bi bwe nii bo na do kange fuloka nobo leme.
\v 11 Di di nuwe digewo digewo nyer. Con yoten coti tokki ki danke, wori co bi dom kange Urcalima. Cin tuken liyar kwamaro biyeken nawo.
\v 12 La con yiciki nii dur cu bitine kange, ya ca yo liyar na co yilam.
\v 13 Con co, cangace kwob, la yi ciki kom yila kangi, ko tiye kom miye nakom fiya mwen dorcet, mimale yilau.
\v 14 La nobo loce ko co, cin twom nob bwiko cek ki manya ciya ti niwo a ca ciyar dor nyer.
\v 15 La ci ne nii wo liyoro, kambo co bou lo weri co tomi ki ciya cucine ne congetini na co nyomom kiyemero co ne ciyeu ki ciya yila kalakangtiyeu.
\v 16 Wi kabako be cinen ki Teluwe fam mwem bo we ma fiya mwen dorcet, fambo kwob.
\v 17 Liya yi co ki dong dong canga ken, wuri mo, maken dor dike bi dure, man nenen tako cunnucut do kwob.
\v 18 Na yobe ce bo yitiki fam mwembo Teluwe ma fiya mwembo fam bo nung.
\v 19 Liya yicoki tom cunnukirning mwo tamciko.
\v 20 Na taarece bo yitiki, fam mwembo wo man yo ken co yora mor kulene,
\v 21 man nuwa tai mwe to, wori mor ni funere, moki to tike mo yobe, mo biye dige mo fii be.
\v 22 Liya yi co ki ki ker mwer ma mamwer bo langtiye, mwo cange bwit mo nyomon moki mo man nii maki to re dike ma yobe,
\v 23 ye bwi mo yobo ki kye miro fiye bini kiyeme no bwiko ma bori na yo co ki mwen.
\v 24 Liya yi nobo tin wiye, kom yom fam bo co tan cike, kom niken niwo ki fam bo kwobbe.
\v 25 Ciki Teluwe, wii ki fam bo kwob.
\v 26 Miki niwo ki dikereri, cin yok cinen ten, niwo man cikeri an yom tangnin bo cine nen.
\v 27 Ki nobo biro koki yilare liya ciye kom bo ki ci fiyemi wii na twallangum ci fo kami.
\v 28 La kambo co to kan nyeri cui ken Urcelima.
\v 29 Kambo cibo bidom kange Betafaji kange Betani dor bange ci coti ki zaitun, co tom nob bwangka coko nyo yob.
\v 30 Yi ciki, kom ya cuinukur do wureno ka kome. No com yari kanto be gelba kange tekum we kom kwiu. Kom bou men ciko.
\v 31 No nii kange me kom ki, 'Ye bwiyi kom kwi tiyeri? kom yi co ki teruwe cuitiye.
\v 32 Nobo biro cu tom ciyeu yaci, fiya be gelba na wo Yeecu yiciyeu.
\v 33 Kambo ci kwi be gelba tiyeri, nob gelba me ciki, ye bwi ci kwi gelba tiye?
\v 34 Ciki teluwe cuii tiye.
\v 35 Ci bo Yeecu nin ciko, cin miti kuleu ciye ro dor be gelba, co ci kun Yeecu ci yoti dorcere.
\v 36 Kambo yaken tiyeri cimiten kulen ciyero ti dor nure
\v 37 Di con dedom yirakako kong zaitun, la nob tomange ceu cin ter bilantumbo ci wab kwamati ki diro dur wori nangeu nyo mamka ci to we.
\v 38 Bibwiyer lamiyo fiye liya wiyewo boti den Tere fuwor neret firen dii kwama kange yorkako wo na duk kakoce.
\v 39 Kangum Fariciyawa mor nob mwe kanka nyico ki ni murangka kwanan nob bwingka mweko.
\v 40 Yeecu yilci miyikum bi rin keti bwenteno nobo biro kumom di terentiyo ki bwiyici ciya bi lange
\v 41 Fiya Yeecu bou bidomri la ci lam bero cori la com ciwiyeu dor cer
\v 42 tok ki, waki kom nyomom dike abou ti ki furnare di dila cumom nuwi kime mani ka to ti.
\v 43 Dila diye boli mwinen, wo nob ki Yeecu mwe, ciyan mu ki yalange kentangum nen, ciyan kwenang mwenten culang ko gwam.
\v 44 Ciyan kun kom bitine wari kange bi beiyo lomwe. Mani ciya dob kange terti dor kecer wori mo kabo bati fiya kwama cwinco tiken nenen.
\v 45 Yeecu do bicor wabe co la tir yuwanob miyankake,
\v 46 yi ci ti ki mulangum mulange lomi a yila lo diko, kom yilam bwak nob kwiyeb.
\v 47 Yeecu wi merang kang kang mor bikur waber. Dila dur wabero kange nob mulanka kange nobo dor noberoci cwiti na ci twallumco.
\v 48 Di la ci fiya bo nor maka, wori nobo cuwati ti cinen kambo ken.
\c 20
\p 
\v 1 Kange diye Yeecu merangti mor bi kurwabe, la tok furen kereuti nubo wabereu kange nubo dur ko.
\v 2 Ci tokeroti ciye coti yiyo kibi kwan kero wini mon mam nan do wotiye. We nenen bi gwamdo woo.
\v 3 La co ciya ciki meki kero mangmekom tiye nyo.
\v 4 kange yuka mwen Yohana yerau di kaka nii fire nenka?
\v 5 Cin kobkanti, bwetici ciki tonou biki di kwamari anyiki yebwe bo nebo birinke cinenen.
\v 6 Na la duwareu bi yi biki nifiro nendi no bo gwam cinye mobangbe ki ter, wori cin ciya mor mereciye Yohana nii to mange
\v 7 Cin ciya ciki yombo keno ki no feri.
\v 8 Yeecu yi ciki moken nyo mani yikamti keno kibo gwando wini ma man dike biromtiye.
\v 9 Yi dubo danke wo kange nii yunkake inabi co ne kange nom tonen toka takeko conyaken bi ti ne kange ya daranyi kutangnyi.
\v 10 Ki cwakiya bika bituweka ram cuii tom kange ceka ce ayo nob tone bone, beri naci neco mor dikero teige neneu. Di nob tonebo ci bunk, ci yoco kang koni.
\v 11 Tom cenge ce tak ci bungco, cine co dotange, ci yweco kan koni.
\v 12 Tomtange na ta'ar ce cin nuwacine der, cin merkeco kare.
\v 13 La nii take Inabi ki, nye ina matiye? ma tom bi bweni macui.
\v 14 Dila nob tone bo toco citokange bwitici, wo co nii coka gwarito bo twallum na kwalito yilam be.
\v 15 Ci mwobken co bwiyim taken cin twallum co. Nyen teeluwen taken Inabi amaciticuke.
\v 16 An bou na twallungum nob take bo wo na yila na neke nubo kenge takeu. Kambo ci nuwanyeri ciki, kwama acukum.
\v 17 La Yeecu toci layiki.
\v 18 Nii wo yar ti dor terero wonineri, an wurorangum. No nii wo tero yelti dorowonineri anfwoyok tamgum co.
\v 19 Ci nob murangkako kange nobo dur waber cin cui naci tomco nawo wori an nyomom ki tokerewo dor ci, la ci cut an rubero.
\v 20 Ci derangecoti cin tom nobo atoutiyeu wor ranyonri nubo weceke, na cifiya lentanke mor lekamor kercono ni, naci nekenco borank kange bi gwam nii dure.
\v 21 Ci meco, ki Nii merangkan nyo yumom muki toka kange meranka dike donge donge tekeu kange nii men nawo dong bwinge kerdiye, muki merangka birin ket dor nure kwama.
\v 22 Mino werfune ka no ya kemer dor kaicar, nin kaka o ong?
\v 23 Yeecu nyomom yulkar yici.
\v 24 Nugmen dinari wuro wee, takeu munranka we dor cereu? ciki, “ki kaicer dike na kaiceroce komne kwama dike na kwace?”
\v 25 Nob murangka kange dur tini nob wabe bere cifiya bo diker bitore mur keu ceroni.
\v 26 nubem. Cin nyemruki ki cuka kan cone, ci tobo kangeker.
\v 27 Kam cadukiyawa cibo ficowege, nobo wo yitiki gwamka tuke mani.
\v 28 Cin meco ciki “nii merangka” Musa mulang nye nen ki, no ni yiki no yini bwi yamdi, nii ki nawe la manki bibwe, nyice anan nawiye, afiya nyicenin bwe.
\v 29 Kakum bi yiten wii niber wo kaboko nab nawe, lam bwe yam menki bwe,
\v 30 Inyo wo yobeu.
\v 31 Wo ta'ar naco, nyo tangka wo nibe re dombo bi beiwi kom cin bweyam.
\v 32 Ki bwili na wiye bwimken.
\v 33 Be diye gwanka duri, wiweco yira tiye. Wori cin nab na weye gwam ciye
\v 34 Yeecu yiciki biberyo dor bi dinene nakangetiye, cine cine citi naka.
\v 35 Nyo kallo wo abou tiyeu, nobo wuro ne bilenke na kwen ka ko ceci nabaruboci manki na ka nawiye.
\v 36 Mani ciya bwi yatiki tok, ciya yilam na biwei tonange kwama.
\v 37 Dila co lam bidom kang bange zaitunedo bei tomangeco lacin teer bi langkako ci cenk lang kwamati ki diro dur. Wori nagen yumankako co mane.
\v 38 Ci ki bi bwiyet atinyo liyowo aboutin mor den tee bei furneret di kwama kanae yor ka la duntanka.
\v 39 Kagum Faricawa bor mwerkanka ciyico ki nii merangka, kwameu nob bwankar mwekoninten.
\v 40 Yeecu ciya ciki, miyikom bi len keti no noboburo kamom di terotinibo andunktange.
\v 41 La Yeecu lambidom ka kange berocori la ciweyeu.
\v 42 Naki kom nyom kakuwo kange dikewo abokimenti ki fawor neredi, naweu cin yurangum nuwe kume.
\v 43 Kakuko we bo ti fiye kom wuyi wo nob kyeb kume bo a mu tiyak tiye, kentangum nen ciyam kwenang mwen ten, culangko gwam.
\v 44 Cin kacimnen bitine wari kange biweiyo Lomewe, ma ciye tob tero kange dor kecer, wuro mo kabo bati fiya kwama cwiti na co fulone neu.
\v 45 Yecu do mor bikurwabe la yuwa nob miyeka.
\v 46 Yi citi ku mulangum mulange Lomi a yila fiye kwobka dilo, di la kom yilam buwak nob kwiyeb.
\v 47 Yecu meranti kang kang mor bikurwaber nebo dor wabero kange nob mulankab kange nobo durko cwiti twallum co. Di la ci fiya bo nure, wori nobo cuwatci ti cinen kambo keu.
\c 21
\p 
\v 1 Yeecu, kun nuweri to nobo cuwe cuwe, buro mer luma mor bala yoka lumak.
\v 2 To kange nawiye bune, fuyai mer aniniyoti yob mor.
\v 3 Bilenke ma yi komti, nawiye bune, fuyai, meri la ciye gwam.
\v 4 Gwam nobo wuro ne luma ciyeke mor cuweka ciye ko tenange nyeu. La nawiye fuyai bune, mor bune ce co merken kiyemer cero gwam, wo co cike.
\v 5 Na wo kamenbo tok ker bikurwabe, kambo ci ma cimen bwayileneu ki tero keneu, neka luma.
\v 6 Dike wo kom to tiye, kakuko wi boti wo tero mani a yito dor kecereu na wo mani a bubatiye.
\v 7 La cin me co ki, Nii “Meranka, fiyan dike wo a bwitiye? Ye a yilam yitom ti na dike borombo na yoten na bwikari?
\v 8 Yeecu ciya, ki kom ti ki bata, kari kange bol kom, diitce an bou mor dene mi, ci yi ti ki, “Man co”, na we dadom, kom bwang cinentende.
\v 9 Tano kom nuwa ker kwenerdi kom kange dii bwali, kom cure, tamyo dike borombo a bwi bwiri, dila cwile mani a boiti nyo na wo.
\v 10 Nyori con yi ci bero an kwenan bero ninten, liyar an kwenan liyaro ninteu.
\v 11 An ma mukaka bitine ko wo tenang tenange fiye ki dimen ki dimen, take an ma wura kange wurolo. An maran yiromtaiyer kange yirombo dur dikwama.
\v 12 Fiya na dike wuro gwam, ciyan tam kom, ci ne kom dotange, ciyan neken kom mor kurbiwaber kange loni furcuna, ciyan boki kom kabom liyare kange nobo durtinim ki ker denemir.
\v 13 A yila kumen fiye ka tokom fulen miro tiye.
\v 14 Ko to fo nerkumer, kom kade batito wo ya ko toktiye.
\v 15 Mo ma nekom kero kange yilendo, wo nob kurome kume gwam, mani ciya dol kobkanka ti kange kome, kaka ci kim kerkume ro.
\v 16 Kange Te, kange yitub, kange naniyak kange farub, ciyan kan kom, ci twallum kangem kumen.
\v 17 Nobo gwam ciyan kokom kiker dene mi.
\v 18 Yiri kume win wo mani a kwob ti,
\v 19 Mor birum nekume kan fiyau dumetinim.
\v 20 Tano kom to Urucalima kentangum ki nobo tee kwentiyeri kom nyomom yarka ceko dadom.
\v 21 Nobo Yahudiya a cu ci yaken diyele kange, nobo tiber cinanlore ciya cu, ciya dobre nobo mwanlore ci dou mor.
\v 22 Kakuko wo na yaka cunere ce, beri dike ci mulange gwam na dim.
\v 23 Kwanci nubo ki fwereu kange nobe ne yir tiyeu mor kumetinwo! Annuwa dotange kambo ken wo tenang tenange bitinim. Ki funer fiye nobo wo wiye.
\v 24 Ciyan yari ki caka kulener take a yaken ki ci canga bitine nin gwam, nobo manki kwama an duwarangum Urucalima ya ciko fiya nobo nyombo kwama ciye a dinitiye
\v 25 Atan yirombo mor kakuke kange cwiyak, kange bitiren. Dorbitine tak nobo nyombo kwama cin nuwa dotange, fwer ciyero an burom temi dir mwenger wima.
\v 26 No a fumom ki ten kange kwaka neret dike a bwi dorbitinero, min. An mok kibikwam dii kwamaro.
\v 27 Nimde ciyan to bibwe Nifire bo ti mor bilore ki bi kwan kange. Duktankako dur.
\v 28 Dila nimde dike wuro ci ter bwikari. Kweni timtiye, la kun dor kumero dii, wori fuloka kumeko dadom.
\v 29 Yeecu ne dangke, “To tii nyencen do kange tiini gwam.
\v 30 Na ci ter fu ka laluko, kan tom ki bwikom, komki Tirakko dadom tak.
\v 31 Nyo tano kom to dike wuro ter bwikakori, kom nyomom liyar kwamaro dadom.
\v 32 Bilenke ma yi kom ti kaldo wo mani a cuti, dike wuro an bwi gwam.
\v 33 Dii kok kange bitini an cum dila kermiro mani a cuti.
\v 34 Di kom kom ka bati ki dor kume, kati kom ne nerkumero tutum ki kwomka dorbitinero kange norangka, kange komka kwarcek. Dila kakuko an bo bati man.
\v 35 Mwinin cito. Dila an bo dor nober gwam wo kwarce tikob dor bitinero nin gwam.
\v 36 Dila kom yi ki bati kang kang, kom kwob diloti bena kom fiya bi kwam do ka torum dike woti gwam a bwitiye, kange kambo katimti kabum Bibwe Nifire”.
\v 37 Ki kakuk, ki merangi mor bikurwabe, kume del yakenti bang ci cotiki zaitune.
\v 38 Nobo gwam tura yaka fiye co wiyeki bwiri cin nowa co bikur waber.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 Na wo nyori, duklume ma ci ca cari to yoten diker kunkar wiyeu, ci cuwoti yabkau dadom.
\v 2 Liyab wabebo kange nob mulangkabo, cin mwerkan dor, na ci fiya ci twalum Yeecu, La ci nuwa tai nibeti.
\v 3 La bwekelkele dokenmor Yahuda Iccariyati, wo wiin mor kwob culombo yobeu.
\v 4 Yahuda ya Liyab wabebo kange nabarub kwenebo nin, cin tokkangi kambo ca miyam Yeecu ti cineneu.
\v 5 Cin bilangi, takeu cin ciya ciyan ne co kyemer.
\v 6 Con ciya, La co do nurewo ca nekeng co ti cinen neu wo kebo tiber nubereu.
\v 7 
\v 8 Nyori Yecu twom Bituru kange yuwana, yici ti, “kom ya ko ka bati cari yabka ko, wo ba catiye.
\v 9 Cin yii co, “Fee mu cwiti nyo ka bati cuwe?”
\v 10 Con ciya ci, “to no kom doken cinar lor di, kange wabkan nii kangetum ki tabwir mwenger, ko bwanten co luwe ca domtiye.
\v 11 “Ko yii nii luwe kom ki, “nii meranka yinen “fe ku fabubeu, fiye ma cam cari ti kange bi bei tomange me?”
\v 12 Can nung kimen kuwe dur ywelum ywela dii. Kom ka batiyo wi.
\v 13 La cin ya, cin fiya dong-dong na wo co yii ciye, cin kam bati cari yabkako.
\v 14 Fiya ca ka cariko lam, con yiken kange bi bei tomange ceu.
\v 15 Con yii ci, “mi dilanti ducce nan ca corito wo kange kom, nyim re nan nuwa, dotange.
\v 16 min yi kom, “ma ma cati tak yaken ciko bi diye Liyar kwama a dim tiye.
\v 17 Yeecu tu kweleu, bwikoko ca ne buka kange ri, cin tiki, “tu wo na kom tikangum bwiti kime.
\v 18 Min yi kom man ma no mwem bi tutti ti tak yaken ciko bi diye Liyar kwamaro a boutiye,
\v 19 Yeecu tu carito bwiko ca bu kange ri con wulangum cin neci, yi ci ti, “wo bwimi ci ne komme, ko ma wo na bulanka mi ko ce.
\v 20 Cin tu kweleu bwiko cariko, con toki, “kwele wo na norro fwir ceu, bwiyale mi wo ci a corti ker kimereu.
\v 21 Dii ko ti yora, kang niwo ko a miye, ye tiye wii kange mo fiye caka cari.
\v 22 Bi bwe nifire an cu na wo ci yowe. La kwannen mo nii wo ma miye tiyeu.
\v 23 La cin yoten ci ti tokkangi bwitici we nii curo a miye co tiye.
\v 24 Kwalkange kwenu more ciye dor, we nii na dure.
\v 25 Con yi ci, Liyab nubo nyombo kwama, teluwe dor cir kange buro ki bi kwang kere dor cireu, ciki cuwo ci ki nubo ma dikero keng tiye.
\v 26 Mani a yilati nyo kange kom, nyori nii wo na dur more kime ri a yilam bwe biduware, kange nii wo yori La gwammeu, a yilam canga.
\v 27 Nyori wo na dur gwammeu, co ci yime kaka na wo canga makimen nangen tiye?
\v 28 Kimeu kom kange mo, cuwa mik.
\v 29 Min yoti kom dor liyarek na wo temi yoti ye dor Liyareu,
\v 30 na ko ca, nako no kange mo, mor Liyare mi, kom yi kutile dumbo kwob culombo yob wo Iciraila ceu.
\v 31 Siman, siman, bulangi, Bwekelkele do a neco mo, na co kwom nen na bi kate.
\v 32 Min kwob mwen dilo bilenkere mwe a yarde, no mo yilau tak ri, ne keb mwebo be kwamer.
\v 33 Bituru yi co, “teluwe min kam bati man ya kange mo Fucina kange bwar.
\v 34 Yeecu yi co, “min yii neng Bituru, fiya na bicake mob kiyange ri, mwan ko nyomka mik kiriti taar.
\v 35 La Yeecu yi ci, “Fiyo cuwo ma twom kom, man ki Liinge, cwaye kime kange tau, ye ka fiya be? Cin ciya co, “Mani”
\v 36 La con yi ci, “caneko, wo ki cwaye kimere ca tu, kange cwaye kulene. Wo man ki yari ca miyem belle ce ca tiyenu.
\v 37 Mi yii komti, “dike mulangum dor mire an dim.
\v 38 La cin yi co ki, “teluwe, to kero kange wo yob”. Con yi ci, “La dim”.
\v 39 Yecu cu bang zaitun na wo ciki mare, bi bei tomange ce bwanten co.
\v 40 La ci Lamri, Yecu yi ci, “kom kwob dilo kati kom doken mor cuwaka.
\v 41 Con dubam ci kutanbo yora, con cunken bitine, kwob dilo,
\v 42 ki. “Te no mun ciya ri, tum kwele wo minen, kebo cwika mik, womweu a mani.
\v 43 La bi bwe tomange kwama wusake cerkangu dii cinen, neco bikwanti.
\v 44 La co mor dotange dur, con yokten kwobka diloko, La mukti cero yilam na bwiyale yaru ti bitine.
\v 45 La con kwenu fiye kwobka diloko nin, con yilaken fiye bi bei tomange ce nin. Co fiya ci da dumti wori ciki fir neret.
\v 46 Con me ci, “Ye bwi ki da dumtiye? Ko kwen ko kwob dilo kati kom doken mor cuwala.
\v 47 Co tok kero ti wiri, nubo ducce cerkangu kange Yahuda, wiin mor kwob culombo yobe ti cinen kaba. Con bou bidom kange Yecu con korkan co.
\v 48 La Yecu yi co “Yahuda, muki miye bi bwe nifire ki kor kanka ka?”
\v 49 La nubo woro wari kange Yecu to dike wo bwitiye ri, cii ki, “teluwe nyo to ci ki kuleng ka?”
\v 50 La wiin more ciye to canga liya wabe, to cewo caktiyereu mwatam.
\v 51 Yecu ki, “Cuwati nyo”, con ke tu ceu, nyori twam”.
\v 52 Yecu yi liya nob wabe kange nubo durko bi kur kwamareu kange nubo durko ci ciya co beu, 'ki, ka ceru ki kulenti kange danti ka ta nii kuye ka?
\v 53 Fiya cuwa mika kom kang-kang mor bi kur kwama reu ka yo bo kang minen. Wo kakuk kimek, kange bikwan kumtacile.
\v 54 Cin tam co, cin yaken ki co Lo nii wabe durko. Bituru bwen cinen ti kutang.
\v 55 Biko ci kwerum kira tiber lor bolange reu, cin cin yironken yiye, Bituru yiken tiber ciyer.
\v 56 Kange nawiye canga to co, wori ci yim cunga kirak, con to co ti con toki, “Nii wuro wii kange co”.
\v 57 La Bituru webkangum, ki nawiye ma nyom cobo.
\v 58 Bi cor di, kange to co, yi ki. “Mo wiin more ciye” Bituru ki “bwayile, ma kebo”
\v 59 Bwiko kene wiineu, kange ywim metenco, “Bilenke, nii wo wii kange co.
\v 60 Bituru ki, nii man nyom bo dike mo tok tiye”, dancan ca dibo tokka kereko bar bi cake mob kiyange.
\v 61 Teluwe, yila to Bituru, La Bituru kwa ki kero Yecu yi ceu, fiya cuwo ci wariyeu, “Fiya na bi cake mob kiyange duwen ri, mwan wengkan ye kiriti taar.
\v 62 Bituru yaken kale cii wiye kambo ken.
\v 63 La nubo ci yo to Yecu tiye buwo malli co.
\v 64 Kambo fini celtiye ri, nubo dur nibero mwerkangi fiye wiin, Liya nob wabe bo kange nob mulangkab, cin doken kico fiye nyime ciye, ciki, “no mo kiritti di yi nyo”
\v 65 La con yi ci, “no nyikom di mani ka ciyati”,
\v 66 Kakaa me kom di kan kar men ti.
\v 67 Min yi ki no mwo Krisiti ri yi nyo, La con yi ci ki “No yi komri mani ka yonmti.
\v 68 Tano mwe kom kerdi mani ka yiye ti
\v 69 Fo ya ciko kab, mi bwe nifire an yiken kanko caktiyer kwama.
\v 70 La gwam ciye cin yi co ki, mo bi bwe kwama ka? Yecu kar cinen “Kom ka tiki nye”.
\v 71 La cin toki, “ye bwi ba do kange warke tiye? Bo ki bwibi ban nuwa nyi co”
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 La mwer kanka ceko gwam kweri cin bouki Yecu kabum Bilatu.
\v 2 Cin teri ci mwel cinen ti, ciki, “nyim fiya nii wo lentang ti ki bi tineu beu, ywam neka dorek ti kaicar nin la ciki toki ciki “Co ki bwico cin kiritti, Liyau”
\v 3 Bilatu me co, ki “Mo liya Yahuda wa ka?” Yecu ciya cinen ciki “mwi tok nyo”
\v 4 Bilatu yi nob wabebo, dortinibo kange mwer kange kako ducce, “Ma fiyabo bwirang ke nii wonin.
\v 5 Dila ciin tii tokkako ciiki, ci kung nubo nin neer ti, ciki merangi mor Yahuda gwam tabti Galili bou ciki fiye wo nin.
\v 6 La kambo Bilatu nuwa weri, cin me keno Yecu nii Galili ri,
\v 7 kambo ci nyimonki Yecu ki no biten liyare Bilatu weri cin tungken Yecu Bilatu nin, wo ki bwiico yim mor Urucalima ki kumeni curo weu.
\v 8 Fiyawo Hiridu to Yecu, cin bilangi wori ci cui, toka Yecu ti ki kwitangka. Cin nuwa ker dorcerla ci cuiti naci to diker nyimankako Yecu ma tiye.
\v 9 Hiridu merang Yecu kero kila kila dila Yecu karci nen bo ker.
\v 10 Nob wale bo durtini kange nob mulangkabo tii, mwelco ti kibi kwam.
\v 11 Hiridu kange nob kweneb ceko torang Yecu, yila ci buo co. La cin du dinen kwilen do yor yore ricin yilaken kico Bilatu nin.
\v 12 La Hiridu kange Bilatu yilam bifarak ki diye curo, no cin nob kiyeb bwitici.
\v 13 Bilatu la cou nob wabeb durtimbo kange nob liyare bo wari kange nubo duce.
\v 14 La cin yi ci, “Kom bo men ki nii wo na nii lentangti ki nube, la kom to, min merangco kakom ri mi fiya bo bwiranke cinen dor diker wo kom mwelcinen tiyeu
\v 15 Mani, Hiridu ken yila binen ki co, la koto, kange diker mani wo nii wo mani lam bwere.
\v 16 La man macinen bi mwerum nami nyem kang cinen”.
\v 17 La nanger Bilatu na cok Yahuda wa nin nii wiin ki duk lume.
\v 18 Dila gwamce cin kung diiro cuko wiin “ko cu ki nii wo, na ko cok nyinen Barabbal.
\v 19 Barabba nii wo ci dok ken Fucina ki kungka kiyana cinanlor kange twalka nobek.
\v 20 Bilatu yiki ker tak, nui ti naci nyengun kang Yecu.
\v 21 Dila cin kung diro, ciki “kulken co, kulken co”.
\v 22 Cin yici tanre ceu, “Ye bwiye, dikero bwirko wuni nii wo man? ma fiya bo bwiranke wo lam bware cinen. La kambo mi macinen bi mwerume ri man nyengum kang cinen”
\v 23 La cin titen ki duro dur cii cuito na kulken co. Diir cero dok Bilatu ciyaka.
\v 24 La Bilatu ciya kini cero,
\v 25 ciin nyengum kang wo ci meu nin, wo ci dok ken fucina ki kungka kiyancek kange twalka nubeke. Dila cin neken Yecu ki cuika ceko.
\v 26 Kambo ci yaken ti kice ri, cin tam nii kange ciman wo kwane, ci ceru cinan lor, dila cin yo cinen ti kwoblom bwatiyem bo duncer, ci bwangten Yecu.
\v 27 Mwerka nube ko duce kange wo natubo ceu wo ii co Hiridu, ma kang bwaa ti dor cereu.
\v 28 Dila cin yila cinen di, Yecu yiki, “Bi wutobo Urucalima, kom cire wiye dor miirm dila kom cii wiye dor kumer kange dor bibeyo lakumeu.
\v 29 La kom to, kumeni ber wo ciya tok ti ki, “Bi bwiyer ki nubo burombo combulome kange burom bo ci nom bo yiir cero wiyeu.
\v 30 La ciya teri ci yi bangtini ko ti, “Yaru dor nyer' kange dunletini, cumom nyo.
\v 31 La no ci yan ma dikero buroki kwama wo tiyo yibereri, ye a bwi tiye no ci kwicimri?”
\v 32 Nubo kangem bo, nob bwirankereb yob cin yaken kici kange co naci twalci wari.
\v 33 Ki kwama wo ci bou fiye ci cuo ti ki “Kwace duce” wi ci kui co kange nob bwirangkebo yobeu wiin kanko catiyer cer la wiin mok ceko nin.
\v 34 Yecu yi ki, “kwama, yabcinen wori, ci nyombo dike ci ma tiyeu”. La ciin mer dacen, ciin tikangum belle ceu.
\v 35 Nubo tirangum ki toi kambo liyab cebo buwo co ti ken ki “cin cer kangeribo. Ca cer dur cero no cin kiritti kwama, wo ci cokke ri!”
\v 36 Nob kwenebo nung co ken, bouti cinen, cine co mwembo fuwar ti,
\v 37 ciki toki ki “No mo liya Yahudawari cer dor mwero”.
\v 38 La yirome wi dor ceer, “Wo co liya Yahudawa”.
\v 39 Wiin mor nob bwirangke wo ci kulken ci wari yeu to co ki “Mwi kebo kiritti ya? cer dor mwero kange nyo”.
\v 40 Dila wincu werank co, ki, “Mani mwi cua tai kwama, kambo mwi mor bolang bwarek ko dong-dong kange ca?
\v 41 Be bifo weu dong-dong, wori bi ki yo diker date kange dike bi mane. Dila nii wo mabo dikero kange yorbe”
\v 42 La coki, “Yecu, kwi kimo no miw bou mor liyar mwek ri
\v 43 Yecu yi co ki “Bilenke ma yinenti, duwen mwan yi kange mo mor dii kwama”.
\v 44 La ki kwama wo kan kene ko nukkune, la kumta ciliu cumom dor bitinero gwam yaken cuko kang kene ko teer,
\v 45 kambo meu dome ri, yilanko mor bikur kwama re woran more yob.
\v 46 Ki wiye ki diro dur Yecu yiki, “Te, min neken dumemi kang mwek”, kambo ci tok we ri, cin bwiyam.
\v 47 La kambo nii dur nob kwenebe to diker maneri cin duktang kwama, ciki, “bicom, wo nii cak-cake”.
\v 48 Ki kwama mwer kangka nobo duce wo bou na ci to dikero bi mane ri, cin yilaken ci kwa cang-cang ti.
\v 49 Dila nubo gwam wo nyumom ce, kange natubo bwangu co Galili yeu, cin tim kutan, cii to dikero buroti.
\v 50 La nii kange wi dendo ki Yucufu, wo wii mor nobo dure. Cin nii ken, ri cin nii cak-cake.
\v 51 Nii wo ciyabo kange dikero ci fuwa kangeu kakaa dikero ci mancu. Ci ceru Arimatiya, bi ten Yahuda, la ciki nintang liyar kwamak.
\v 52 Nii wo, ya Bilatu nin, la cin keni na neco curen bwi Yecu.
\v 53 Cin cuku, cin cumon ki yilank linin ko ken. La cin yoken mor tuwe wo ci cuwe cuwe mor tere, wo ci fwerum bo nii wi yeu.
\v 54 Kakuko co kakuk ywelkak, la kakuk fobka Yahudawa ko dadum.
\v 55 Natubo wo bou kange Yecu Galili ye bwangten lacintom tuweu. Kange kambo ci yom bwi ceu.
\v 56 Cin yilaken la cin ywellang kwilendo Ficange kange nuwang. La ki diye fobka Yahudawak ri cin fubom nawo werfundo to keu
\c 24
\p 
\v 1 Ki kwomje kikume kume niberece cin bo tuwenim, cinbouki kulen tuika kuneko ficang ficang woci ywelleu.
\v 2 Ci fiya tero tun ken tunngen cunge tuwek.
\v 3 Cin doken morece, dilaci fiyabo bwi Yeecu.
\v 4 Inbwiu kambo cimor kwobtangka dikekebwiuweri, nubo yob tirarim kabumci ki kulendo fuwe cukcukke.
\v 5 La natubowo cunken ki dorciro bitine worintai, cin yo natuno, “yebwi komdo nikidumeti nor buware?
\v 6 Manifo lan kwennum! kambo ci yimko ker ki kwamawo ci Galili, intoki,
\v 7 ciyan nekan bi bwe niffire kang nob bwiran keb la ciyan yei kenco, kikume taare ankwenumtak”.
\v 8 La natubo kwaki kercero!
\v 9 Lacin dubom tuweu cin yilakeng laciyi kwobculombo winneuwuro dekero birombo kanngu tangneu gwamm.
\v 10 Maryamu magdaliya, yuwana, Maryamu ne Yakubu, kan'nge tangne natubo ci wariyeu cine nob toman'ngeb cebo fulen dikorowuro bwiyeu.
\v 11 Dila nobtoman'ngebcebo tu kero muni kebo diker maka nangenek, dila cinebo bilinke natubowonin.
\v 12 Kwarub kan'nge wo Bituru kweni, cwayya tuwenin, cunken torang moreuti, lacinto lalanggo fuworgo kikwace. Lana nyime Bituru yaken loco, lata nyimang di bweweuti.
\v 13 Kikakucori, inwonyo yob wo more yakanti cinarloro kan'nge dende Imawu wuro kutankaceko nan.
\v 14 Citi fuwakan'ngi ko bwitici kangediwo yaa bwiweu.
\v 15 Yilam kambo ci fuwakamti wari kange meka kerekeri, Yeecu ki bwico boubidom cinen yakenti kanyeci.
\v 16 La nuweceu dolbo nyobkaceko.
\v 17 “Yeecu yici, inye kom tokkerti dorcere kambo kom yakentiyeu?” Cintinwifiyeco laci cii bwatumbotiwi.
\v 18 Kaci tun kan'nge morece nendo kiliyobac, lan ciya cinen, “Mwowin cwar niwo Wurcalima wo nyombo dike birombo bwiuwe firen kikabake ki kumenicuo?
\v 19 Yeecu yico, “bikulentito wini?” Cin ciyaco, dikerotin kan'nge Yeecu bwe Nazaret, wuro buwe tomanye, woki dikerotinimbo dur, kan'nge kertinimbo dur fiye kwama wiyeu kan'nge nob.
\v 20 Ki ciyaka nob wabero dur kan'nge nob li yareb nyebo ci nekenco naci warco naci kulkentencotak.
\v 21 Dila nyin yoner nyiki cowo a cer Icerelatiyeu. Nyo, nobo nawori, naweu kume Taar dikero birombo bwiuwe.
\v 22 Dila aa di duweno kowo, kamnyum natubembo nyi wariyeu ma nyinen diker nyimankartinim, ki yancimbo tuwe kiburiceu.
\v 23 Kambo ci fiyabo bwiceri, cinbom, ciki cikeneu cinto dukum nobtomanyebo burombo yici ki wi kedume.
\v 24 Kannyum nabarob wuro wari kannye nyeu cinya tuwenin, yafi kwabti nawo natubo tokeu. Dila ci tocibo.
\v 25 Yeecu yici ki, “Kom nob kuleneb nubo nebo bilinke dor dikero nob tomanyeb dukumebo tokeu!
\v 26 Yilabokang kiritti anuwa dotannge dikero biromba, laken mor duktang kaka?”
\v 27 Dila kikab wi mucanim yaken ciko nobtoma'ngobonin kwarub. Yeecu futang cinen dikero kaminge co. Wibe fumertinimbonin gwamm.
\v 28 Kambo cilam cinar loroce fiye ci yakenti wuyeri cabunane Yeecu maa nadike muncan cuken.
\v 29 Dila cin dokco ki, “yiken kan'ngeci, wori wori meu dadom kakuko do dikati. “La Yeecu ya yiken kan'nge ci.
\v 30 Bwiuki, kambo ciyiken ci naci cacarite, intu Tiilita, kambo ci yoten bibuyer wiyeri, kiyannyi, lanneci.
\v 31 Lamwo nuweceu wumwom, kambo cinyimocin ciri, lalem kaci,
\v 32 Cin yi butice, wendi mani twirangbobo mornerber, kambo citok keroti kan'ngebo dor nurereu, kambo ci wombinen bifumertinnimbeu?”
\v 33 Lacin kweni ki kwamaco, cin yiken wurcalima. Cinfiya culombo wineuwo wari, kan'nge birombo ciwari kan'nge ciyeu,
\v 34 “Ki, kibicom kwama kwenum, inbow cimanin”.
\v 35 Laci tok dikero birombo bwiu nureu, kan'nge kambo ci fwetang cinen Yeecu kambo kiyan Tilita.
\v 36 Kambo citikang dikerobirombo tiyeri, dila Yeecun tii tibercir, dilla yici, “fuwer nerer kumer”.
\v 37 Dilla cin fakla cin dimkitani, cikwatiri cin tom wulo.
\v 38 Yeecu yiciki yebwi kom kwomdortiye? yebiro meke kunouti morner kumere?
\v 39 To kanimiu kan'nge Nanimiu, la muo kan'nye muo. Teiye nakomto. Wulo manki bwi kan'nge yiri, kambo komto nicikeu”.
\v 40 Kamboci tokweri, lacin nung cinen kaniceu kan'nge naniceu.
\v 41 Kamboci dimki fuwer nerereu, kan'nge nyimanka, Yeecu yici, “Komwiki kan'nge cariya?”
\v 42 Lacin neco jinnge belumbeleu.
\v 43 Yeecunyo cam kabumcim.
\v 44 Lanyici, “Kambo miwari kan'nge komeu minyikom miki gwamm nike cimuleng wertun mucar kan'nge nentomanngeb kan'nge zaburau atin dii kang”.
\v 45 Lacin wumwum nerciro naci nyimwom bifumertininbo.
\v 46 Yici, “mulangum mulannge, kiritti annuwa dotange, amkwenum an kwenum tuwe ki kume taare.
\v 47 Komwab dencero kan'nge dobka bwirang kerer mor denece gwamm mor nube, komteri wurucalima.
\v 48 Kom nobwarib dikero birombo.
\v 49 Too, mi twomutiki nor Teemiro dor kumer. Dila kom cini bitinece, catin tunkumen bikwan firen dii.”
\v 50 Lananyime Yeecu yaken wari kna'nyeci yaa cilam Betani. Lankun kanceko yocimeti bibwiyerwi.
\v 51 Yilam kamboci yocinten bibwi yerotiyeri, dubomci lacim tumco cin yakenkico dikwama.
\v 52 Lacin wabco, cin yilarangum wurucalima kifuwor nerer ducce.
\v 53 Kicatec cimor lokwama cine dencore bibwiyerti. 
